4936 void x86Semantics::cmpsw_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
4937 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
4938 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
4939 auto index1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_SI));
4940 auto index2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_DI));
4941 auto cx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_CX));
4942 auto df = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_DF));
4943
4944 /* If the REP prefix is defined, convert REP into REPE */
4945 if (inst.getPrefix() == triton::arch::x86::ID_PREFIX_REP)
4946 inst.setPrefix(triton::arch::x86::ID_PREFIX_REPE);
4947
4948 /* Check if there is a REP prefix and a counter to zero */
4949 if (inst.getPrefix() != triton::arch::x86::ID_PREFIX_INVALID && this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(cx)->evaluate().is_zero()) {
4950 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
4951 return;
4952 }
4953
4954 /* Create symbolic operands */
4955 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
4956 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
4957 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, index1);
4958 auto op4 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, index2);
4959 auto op5 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, df);
4960
4961 /* Create the semantics */
4962 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->bvsub(op1, op2);
4963 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->ite(
4964 this->astCtxt->equal(op5, this->astCtxt->bvfalse()),
4965 this->astCtxt->bvadd(op3, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::word, index1.getBitSize())),
4966 this->astCtxt->bvsub(op3, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::word, index1.getBitSize()))
4967 );

4969 this->astCtxt->equal(op5, this->astCtxt->bvfalse()),
4970 this->astCtxt->bvadd(op4, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::word, index2.getBitSize())),
4971 this->astCtxt->bvsub(op4, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::word, index2.getBitSize()))
4972 );
4973

4975 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicVolatileExpression(inst, node1, "CMPSW operation");
4976 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, index1, "Index (SI) operation");

4989 this->sf_s(inst, expr1, dst, true);
4990 this->zf_s(inst, expr1, dst, true);
4991
4992 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
4993 this->controlFlow_s(inst);

4996
4997 void x86Semantics::cmpxchg_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
4998 auto& src1 = inst.operands[0];
4999 auto& src2 = inst.operands[1];
5000
5001 /* Create the tempory accumulator */
5002 triton::arch::OperandWrapper accumulator(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AL));
5003 triton::arch::OperandWrapper accumulatorp(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_AL));
5004
5005 switch (src1.getSize()) {
5006 case triton::size::word:
5007 accumulator.setRegister(arch::Register(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX)));
5008 break;
5009 case triton::size::dword:
5010 accumulator.setRegister(arch::Register(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EAX)));
5011 break;
5012 case triton::size::qword:
5013 accumulator.setRegister(arch::Register(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RAX)));
5014 break;
5015 }
5016
5017 /* Create symbolic operands */
5018 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, accumulator);
5019 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
5020 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
5021 auto op1p = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(accumulatorp);
5022 auto op2p = this->symbolicEngine->getRegisterAst((src1.getType() == triton::arch::OP_REG ? Register(this->architecture->getParentRegister(src1.getRegister())) : accumulatorp.getRegister()));
5023 auto op3p = this->symbolicEngine->getRegisterAst((src1.getType() == triton::arch::OP_REG ? Register(this->architecture->getParentRegister(src2.getRegister())) : accumulatorp.getRegister()));
5024
5025 /* Create the semantics */
5026 auto nodeq = this->astCtxt->equal(op1, op2);
5027 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->bvsub(op1, op2);
5028 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->ite(nodeq, op3, op2);
5029 auto node3 = this->astCtxt->ite(nodeq, op1, op2);
5030 auto node2p = this->astCtxt->ite(nodeq, op3p, op2p);
5031 auto node3p = this->astCtxt->ite(nodeq, op1p, op2p);
5032
5033 /* Create symbolic expression */
5034 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicVolatileExpression(inst, node1, "CMP operation");
5035 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicVolatileExpression(inst, node2, "Temporary operation");
5036 auto expr3 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicVolatileExpression(inst, node2p, "Temporary operation");
5037 auto expr4 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicVolatileExpression(inst, node3, "Temporary operation");
5038 auto expr5 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicVolatileExpression(inst, node3p, "Temporary operation");
5039
5040 triton::engines::symbolic::SharedSymbolicExpression expr6 = nullptr;
5041 triton::engines::symbolic::SharedSymbolicExpression expr7 = nullptr;
5042
5043 /* Destination */
5044 if (nodeq->evaluate() == false && src1.getType() == triton::arch::OP_REG) {
5045 const auto& src1p = this->architecture->getParentRegister(src1.getRegister());
5046 expr6 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicRegisterExpression(inst, node2p, src1p, "XCHG operation");
5047 } else
5048 expr6 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, src1, "XCHG operation");
5049
5050 /* Accumulator */
5051 if (nodeq->evaluate() == true)
5052 expr7 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node3p, accumulatorp, "XCHG operation");
5053 else
5054 expr7 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node3, accumulator, "XCHG operation");
5055
5056 /* Spread taint */
5057 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->isTainted(accumulator) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(src1);
5058 expr2->isTainted = expr1->isTainted;
5059 expr3->isTainted = expr1->isTainted;
5060 expr4->isTainted = expr1->isTainted;
5061 expr5->isTainted = expr1->isTainted;
5062 expr6->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(src1, src2);
5063 expr7->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(accumulator, src1);
5064
5065 /* Update symbolic flags */
5066 this->af_s(inst, expr1, accumulator, op1, op2, true);
5067 this->cfSub_s(inst, expr1, accumulator, op1, op2, true);
5068 this->ofSub_s(inst, expr1, accumulator, op1, op2, true);
5069 this->pf_s(inst, expr1, accumulator, true);
5070 this->sf_s(inst, expr1, accumulator, true);
5071 this->zf_s(inst, expr1, accumulator, true);
5072
5073 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
5074 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
5075 }
5076
5077
5078 void x86Semantics::cmpxchg16b_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
5079 auto& src1 = inst.operands[0];
5080 auto src2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RDX));
5081 auto src3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RAX));
5082 auto src4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RCX));
5083 auto src5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RBX));
5084
5085 /* Create symbolic operands */
5086 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
5087 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
5088 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src3);
5089 auto op4 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src4);
5090 auto op5 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src5);
5091
5092 /* Create the semantics */
5093 /* CMP8B */
5094 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->bvsub(this->astCtxt->concat(op2, op3), op1);
5095 /* Destination */
5096 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(node1, this->astCtxt->bv(0, triton::bitsize::dqword)), this->astCtxt->concat(op4, op5), op1);
5097 /* EDX:EAX */
5098 auto node3 = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(node1, this->astCtxt->bv(0, triton::bitsize::dqword)), this->astCtxt->concat(op2, op3), op1);
5099
5100 /* Create symbolic expression */
5101 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicVolatileExpression(inst, node1, "CMP operation");
5102 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, src1, "XCHG16B memory operation");
5103 auto expr3 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, this->astCtxt->extract(127, 64, node3), src2, "XCHG16B RDX operation");
5104 auto expr4 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, this->astCtxt->extract(63, 0, node3), src3, "XCHG16B RAX operation");
5105
5106 /* Spread taint */
5107 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->isTainted(src1) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(src2) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(src3);
5108 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->setTaint(src1, this->taintEngine->isTainted(src2) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(src3));
5109 expr3->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(src2, src1);
5110 expr4->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(src3, src1);
5111
5112 /* Update symbolic flags */
5113 this->zf_s(inst, expr1, src1, true);
5114
5115 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
5116 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
5117 }

5119
5120 void x86Semantics::cmpxchg8b_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
5121 auto& src1 = inst.operands[0];
5122 auto src2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EDX));
5123 auto src3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EAX));
5124 auto src4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ECX));
5125 auto src5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EBX));
5126 auto src2p = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_EDX));
5127 auto src3p = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_EAX));
5128
5129 /* Create symbolic operands */
5130 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
5131 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
5132 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src3);
5133 auto op4 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src4);
5134 auto op5 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src5);
5135 auto op2p = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2p);
5136 auto op3p = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src3p);
5137
5138 /* Create the semantics */
5139 /* CMP8B */
5140 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->bvsub(this->astCtxt->concat(op2, op3), op1);
5141 /* Destination */
5142 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(node1, this->astCtxt->bv(0, triton::bitsize::qword)), this->astCtxt->concat(op4, op5), op1);
5143 /* EDX:EAX */
5144 auto node3 = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(node1, this->astCtxt->bv(0, triton::bitsize::qword)), this->astCtxt->concat(op2, op3), op1);
5145 auto node3p = this->astCtxt->ite(
5146 this->astCtxt->equal(
5147 node1,
5148 this->astCtxt->bv(0, triton::bitsize::qword)),
5149 this->astCtxt->concat(op2p, op3p),
5150 this->astCtxt->zx(src2p.getBitSize() + src3p.getBitSize() - src1.getBitSize(), op1)
5151 );
5152
5153 /* Create symbolic expression */
5154 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicVolatileExpression(inst, node1, "CMP operation");
5155 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, src1, "XCHG8B memory operation");
5156 auto expr3 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicVolatileExpression(inst, node3, "Temporary operation");
5157 auto expr4 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicVolatileExpression(inst, node3p, "Temporary operation");
5158
5159 triton::engines::symbolic::SharedSymbolicExpression expr5 = nullptr;
5160 triton::engines::symbolic::SharedSymbolicExpression expr6 = nullptr;
5161
5162 /* EDX */
5163 if (node1->evaluate() == 0)
5164 expr5 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, this->astCtxt->extract((src2p.getBitSize() * 2 - 1), src2p.getBitSize(), node3p), src2p, "XCHG8B EDX operation");
5165 else
5166 expr5 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, this->astCtxt->extract(63, 32, node3), src2, "XCHG8B EDX operation");
5167
5168 /* EAX */
5169 if (node1->evaluate() == 0)
5170 expr6 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, this->astCtxt->extract(src2p.getBitSize() - 1, 0, node3p), src3p, "XCHG8B EAX operation");
5171 else
5172 expr6 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, this->astCtxt->extract(31, 0, node3), src3, "XCHG8B EAX operation");
5173
5174 /* Spread taint */
5175 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->isTainted(src1) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(src2) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(src3);
5176 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->setTaint(src1, this->taintEngine->isTainted(src2) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(src3));
5177 expr3->isTainted = this->taintEngine->isTainted(src1) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(src2) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(src3);
5178 expr4->isTainted = this->taintEngine->isTainted(src1) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(src2) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(src3);
5179 expr5->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(src2, src1);
5180 expr6->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(src3, src1);
5181
5182 /* Update symbolic flags */
5183 this->zf_s(inst, expr1, src1, true);
5184
5185 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
5186 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
5187 }

5189
5190 void x86Semantics::cpuid_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
5191 auto src = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
5192 auto dst1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
5193 auto dst2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_BX));
5194 auto dst3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_CX));
5195 auto dst4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_DX));
5196
5197 /* Create symbolic operands */
5198 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
5199
5200 /* Create the semantics */
5201 triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode node1 = nullptr;
5202 triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode node2 = nullptr;
5203 triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode node3 = nullptr;
5204 triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode node4 = nullptr;
5205
5206 /* In this case, we concretize the AX option */
5207 switch (static_cast<triton::uint32>(op1->evaluate())) {
5208 case 0:
5209 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x0000000d, dst1.getBitSize());
5210 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x756e6547, dst2.getBitSize());
5211 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x6c65746e, dst3.getBitSize());
5212 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x49656e69, dst4.getBitSize());
5213 break;
5214 case 1:
5215 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x000306a9, dst1.getBitSize());
5216 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x02100800, dst2.getBitSize());
5217 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x7fbae3ff, dst3.getBitSize());
5218 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0xbfebfbff, dst4.getBitSize());
5219 break;
5220 case 2:
5221 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x76035a01, dst1.getBitSize());
5222 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00f0b2ff, dst2.getBitSize());
5223 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst3.getBitSize());
5224 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00ca0000, dst4.getBitSize());
5225 break;
5226 case 3:
5227 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst1.getBitSize());
5228 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst2.getBitSize());
5229 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst3.getBitSize());
5230 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst4.getBitSize());
5231 break;
5232 case 4:
5233 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x1c004121, dst1.getBitSize());
5234 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x01c0003f, dst2.getBitSize());
5235 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x0000003f, dst3.getBitSize());
5236 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst4.getBitSize());
5237 break;
5238 case 5:
5239 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000040, dst1.getBitSize());
5240 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000040, dst2.getBitSize());
5241 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000003, dst3.getBitSize());
5242 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00021120, dst4.getBitSize());
5243 break;
5244 case 0x80000000:
5245 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x80000008, dst1.getBitSize());
5246 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst2.getBitSize());
5247 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst3.getBitSize());
5248 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst4.getBitSize());
5249 break;
5250 case 0x80000001:
5251 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst1.getBitSize());
5252 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst2.getBitSize());
5253 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000001, dst3.getBitSize());
5254 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x28100800, dst4.getBitSize());
5255 break;
5256 case 0x80000002:
5257 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x20202020, dst1.getBitSize());
5258 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x49202020, dst2.getBitSize());
5259 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x6c65746e, dst3.getBitSize());
5260 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x20295228, dst4.getBitSize());
5261 break;
5262 case 0x80000003:
5263 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x65726f43, dst1.getBitSize());
5264 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x294d5428, dst2.getBitSize());
5265 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x2d376920, dst3.getBitSize());
5266 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x30323533, dst4.getBitSize());
5267 break;
5268 case 0x80000004:
5269 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x5043204d, dst1.getBitSize());
5270 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x20402055, dst2.getBitSize());
5271 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x30392e32, dst3.getBitSize());
5272 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x007a4847, dst4.getBitSize());
5273 break;
5274 case 0x80000005:
5275 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst1.getBitSize());
5276 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst2.getBitSize());
5277 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst3.getBitSize());
5278 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst4.getBitSize());
5279 break;
5280 case 0x80000006:
5281 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst1.getBitSize());
5282 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst2.getBitSize());
5283 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x01006040, dst3.getBitSize());
5284 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst4.getBitSize());
5285 break;
5286 case 0x80000007:
5287 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst1.getBitSize());
5288 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst2.getBitSize());
5289 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst3.getBitSize());
5290 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000100, dst4.getBitSize());
5291 break;
5292 case 0x80000008:
5293 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00003024, dst1.getBitSize());
5294 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst2.getBitSize());
5295 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst3.getBitSize());
5296 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst4.getBitSize());
5297 break;
5298 default:
5299 node1 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000007, dst1.getBitSize());
5300 node2 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000340, dst2.getBitSize());
5301 node3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000340, dst3.getBitSize());
5302 node4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0x00000000, dst4.getBitSize());
5303 break;
5304 }
5305
5306 /* Create symbolic expression */
5307 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, dst1, "CPUID AX operation");
5308 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, dst2, "CPUID BX operation");
5309 auto expr3 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node3, dst3, "CPUID CX operation");
5310 auto expr4 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node4, dst4, "CPUID DX operation");
5311
5312 /* Spread taint */
5313 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->setTaintRegister(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX), false);
5314 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->setTaintRegister(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_BX), false);
5315 expr3->isTainted = this->taintEngine->setTaintRegister(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_CX), false);
5316 expr4->isTainted = this->taintEngine->setTaintRegister(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_DX), false);
5317
5318 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
5319 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
5320 }
5321
5322
5323 void x86Semantics::cqo_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
5324 auto dst = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RDX));
5325 auto src = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RAX));
5326
5327 /* Create symbolic operands */
5328 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
5329
5330 /* Create the semantics - TMP = 128 bitvec (RDX:RAX) */
5331 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::qword, op1);
5332
5333 /* Create symbolic expression */
5334 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicVolatileExpression(inst, node1, "Temporary variable");
5335
5336 /* Spread taint */
5337 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->isRegisterTainted(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RAX));
5338
5339 /* Create the semantics - RDX = TMP[127...64] */
5340 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dqword-1, triton::bitsize::qword, this->astCtxt->reference(expr1));
5341
5342 /* Create symbolic expression */
5343 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, dst, "CQO operation");
5344
5345 /* Spread taint */
5346 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
5347
5348 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
5349 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
5350 }
5351
5352
5353 void x86Semantics::cwd_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
5354 auto dst = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_DX));
5355 auto src = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
5356
5357 /* Create symbolic operands */
5358 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
5359
5360 /* Create the semantics - TMP = 32 bitvec (DX:AX) */
5361 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::word, op1);
5362
5363 /* Create symbolic expression */
5364 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicVolatileExpression(inst, node1, "Temporary variable");
5365
5366 /* Spread taint */
5367 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->isRegisterTainted(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
5368
5369 /* Create the semantics - DX = TMP[31...16] */
5370 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dword-1, triton::bitsize::word, this->astCtxt->reference(expr1));
5371
5372 /* Create symbolic expression */
5373 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, dst, "CWD operation");
5374
5375 /* Spread taint */
5376 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
5377
5378 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
5379 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
5380 }

5383 void x86Semantics::cwde_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
5384 auto dst = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EAX));
5385
5386 /* Create symbolic operands */
5387 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
5388
5389 /* Create the semantics */
5390 auto node = this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::word, this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::word-1, 0, op1));
5391
5392 /* Create symbolic expression */
5393 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "CWDE operation");
5394
5395 /* Spread taint */
5396 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, dst);
5397
5398 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
5399 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
5400 }
5401
5402
5403 void x86Semantics::dec_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
5404 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
5405
5406 /* Create symbolic operands */
5407 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
5408 auto op2 = this->astCtxt->bv(1, dst.getBitSize());
5409
5410 /* Create the semantics */
5411 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvsub(op1, op2);
5412
5413 /* Create symbolic expression */
5414 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "DEC operation");
5415
5416 /* Spread taint */
5417 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, dst);
5418
5419 /* Update symbolic flags */
5420 this->af_s(inst, expr, dst, op1, op2);
5421 this->ofSub_s(inst, expr, dst, op1, op2);
5422 this->pf_s(inst, expr, dst);
5423 this->sf_s(inst, expr, dst);
5424 this->zf_s(inst, expr, dst);
5425
5426 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
5427 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
5428 }
5429
5430
5431 void x86Semantics::div_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
5432 auto& src = inst.operands[0];
5433
5434 /* Create symbolic operands */
5435 auto divisor = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
5436
5437 /* Return an exception if the divisor is zero */
5438 if (divisor->evaluate() == 0) {
5439 this->exception = triton::arch::FAULT_DE;
5440 return;
5441 }
5442
5443 /* Create symbolic expression */
5444 switch (src.getSize()) {
5445
5446 case triton::size::byte: {
5447 /* AX */
5448 auto ax = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
5449 auto dividend = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ax);
5450 /* res = AX / Source */
5451 auto result = this->astCtxt->bvudiv(dividend, this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::byte, divisor));
5452 /* mod = AX % Source */
5453 auto mod = this->astCtxt->bvurem(dividend, this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::byte, divisor));
5454 /* AH = mod */
5455 /* AL = res */
5456 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(
5457 this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::byte - 1), 0, mod), /* AH = mod */
5458 this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::byte - 1), 0, result) /* AL = res */
5459 );
5460 /* Create symbolic expression */
5461 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, ax, "DIV operation");
5462 /* Apply the taint */
5463 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(ax, src);
5464 break;
5465 }
5466
5467 case triton::size::word: {
5468 /* DX:AX */
5469 auto dx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_DX));
5470 auto ax = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
5471 auto dividend = this->astCtxt->concat(this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dx), this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ax));
5472 /* res = DX:AX / Source */
5473 auto result = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::word - 1), 0, this->astCtxt->bvudiv(dividend, this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::word, divisor)));
5474 /* mod = DX:AX % Source */
5475 auto mod = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::word - 1), 0, this->astCtxt->bvurem(dividend, this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::word, divisor)));
5476 /* Create the symbolic expression for AX */
5477 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, result, ax, "DIV operation");
5478 /* Apply the taint for AX */
5479 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(ax, src);
5480 /* Create the symbolic expression for DX */
5481 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, mod, dx, "DIV operation");
5482 /* Apply the taint for DX */
5483 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dx, src);
5484 break;
5485 }
5486
5487 case triton::size::dword: {
5488 /* EDX:EAX */
5489 auto edx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EDX));
5490 auto eax = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EAX));
5491 auto dividend = this->astCtxt->concat(this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, edx), this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, eax));
5492 /* res = EDX:EAX / Source */
5493 auto result = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::dword - 1), 0, this->astCtxt->bvudiv(dividend, this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword, divisor)));
5494 /* mod = EDX:EAX % Source */
5495 auto mod = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::dword - 1), 0, this->astCtxt->bvurem(dividend, this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword, divisor)));
5496 /* Create the symbolic expression for EAX */
5497 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, result, eax, "DIV operation");
5498 /* Apply the taint for EAX */
5499 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(eax, src);
5500 /* Create the symbolic expression for EDX */
5501 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, mod, edx, "DIV operation");
5502 /* Apply the taint for EDX */
5503 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(edx, src);
5504 break;
5505 }
5506
5507 case triton::size::qword: {
5508 /* RDX:RAX */
5509 auto rdx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RDX));
5510 auto rax = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RAX));
5511 auto dividend = this->astCtxt->concat(this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, rdx), this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, rax));
5512 /* res = RDX:RAX / Source */
5513 auto result = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::qword - 1), 0, this->astCtxt->bvudiv(dividend, this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::qword, divisor)));
5514 /* mod = RDX:RAX % Source */
5515 auto mod = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::qword - 1), 0, this->astCtxt->bvurem(dividend, this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::qword, divisor)));
5516 /* Create the symbolic expression for RAX */
5517 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, result, rax, "DIV operation");
5518 /* Apply the taint for EAX */
5519 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(rax, src);
5520 /* Create the symbolic expression for RDX */
5521 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, mod, rdx, "DIV operation");
5522 /* Apply the taint for EDX */
5523 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(rdx, src);
5524 break;
5525 }
5526
5527 }
5528
5529 /* Tag undefined flags */
5530 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AF));
5531 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_CF));
5532 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_OF));
5533 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_PF));
5534 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_SF));
5535 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ZF));
5536
5537 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
5538 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
5539 }
5540
5541
5542 void x86Semantics::endbr32_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
5543 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
5544 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
5545 }
5546
5547
5548 void x86Semantics::endbr64_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
5549 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
5550 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
5551 }
5552
5553
5554 void x86Semantics::extractps_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
5555 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
5556 auto& src1 = inst.operands[1];
5557 auto& src2 = inst.operands[2];
5558
5559 /* Create symbolic operands */
5560 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
5561 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
5562
5563 /* Create the semantics */
5564 auto node = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dword-1, 0,
5565 this->astCtxt->bvlshr(
5566 op2,
5567 this->astCtxt->bvmul(
5568 this->astCtxt->zx(126, this->astCtxt->extract(1, 0, op3)),
5569 this->astCtxt->bv(triton::bitsize::dword, triton::bitsize::dqword)
5570 )
5571 )
5572 );
5573
5574 switch (dst.getBitSize()) {
5575 case triton::bitsize::dword:
5576 break;
5577 case triton::bitsize::qword:
5578 node = this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword, node);
5579 break;
5580 default:
5581 throw triton::exceptions::Semantics("x86Semantics::extractps_s(): Invalid destination operand.");
5582 }
5583
5584 /* Create symbolic expression */
5585 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "EXTRACTPS operation");
5586
5587 /* Spread taint */
5588 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src1);
5589
5590 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
5591 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
5592 }
5593
5594
5595 void x86Semantics::fxrstor_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
5596 /* Fetch the current architecture */
5597 auto arch = this->architecture->getArchitecture();
5598
5599 /* Determine if we are executing in 64 bit mode */
5600 auto is64bits = arch == triton::arch::architecture_e::ARCH_X86_64;
5601
5602 /* Fetch the memory operand */
5603 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
5604 auto& mem = dst.getMemory();
5605 auto m512byte = mem.getAddress();
5606
5607 /* Check if the address is on a 16-byte boundary */
5608 if (m512byte & 0xF) {
5609 this->exception = triton::arch::FAULT_GP;
5610 return;
5611 }
5612
5613 /* Fetch the FPU, STX, SSE, EFER and CS implicit operands */
5614 auto fcw = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FCW));
5615 auto fsw = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FSW));
5616 auto ftw = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FTW));
5617 auto fop = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FOP));
5618 auto fip = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FIP));
5619 auto fcs = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FCS));
5620 auto fdp = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FDP));
5621 auto fds = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FDS));
5622 auto mxcsr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_MXCSR));
5623 auto mxcsr_mask = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_MXCSR_MASK));
5624 auto st0 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST0));
5625 auto st1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST1));
5626 auto st2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST2));
5627 auto st3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST3));
5628 auto st4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST4));
5629 auto st5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST5));
5630 auto st6 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST6));
5631 auto st7 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST7));
5632 auto xmm0 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM0));
5633 auto xmm1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM1));
5634 auto xmm2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM2));
5635 auto xmm3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM3));
5636 auto xmm4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM4));
5637 auto xmm5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM5));
5638 auto xmm6 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM6));
5639 auto xmm7 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM7));
5640 auto ffxsr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EFER_FFXSR));
5641 auto cs = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_CS));
5642
5643 /* Fetch the implicit memory slots for the 'Non-64-bit Mode Layout' */
5644 auto fcw_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 0, fcw.getSize()));
5645 auto fsw_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 2, fsw.getSize()));
5646 auto ftw_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 4, ftw.getSize() / 2));
5647 auto fop_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 6, fop.getSize()));
5648 auto fip_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 8, fip.getSize() / 2));
5649 auto fcs_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 12, fcs.getSize()));
5650 auto fdp_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 16, fdp.getSize() / 2));
5651 auto fds_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 20, fds.getSize()));
5652 auto mxcsr_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 24, mxcsr.getSize()));
5653 auto mxcsr_mask_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 28, mxcsr_mask.getSize()));
5654 auto st0_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 32, st0.getSize()));
5655 auto st1_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 48, st1.getSize()));
5656 auto st2_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 64, st2.getSize()));
5657 auto st3_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 80, st3.getSize()));
5658 auto st4_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 96, st4.getSize()));
5659 auto st5_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 112, st5.getSize()));
5660 auto st6_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 128, st6.getSize()));
5661 auto st7_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 144, st7.getSize()));
5662 auto xmm0_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 160, xmm0.getSize()));
5663 auto xmm1_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 176, xmm1.getSize()));
5664 auto xmm2_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 192, xmm2.getSize()));
5665 auto xmm3_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 208, xmm3.getSize()));
5666 auto xmm4_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 224, xmm4.getSize()));
5667 auto xmm5_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 240, xmm5.getSize()));
5668 auto xmm6_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 256, xmm6.getSize()));
5669 auto xmm7_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 272, xmm7.getSize()));
5670
5671 /* Create the symbolic operands */
5672 auto fcw_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fcw_addr);
5673 auto fsw_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fsw_addr);
5674 auto ftw_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ftw_addr);
5675 auto fop_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fop_addr);
5676 auto fip_ast = this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword, this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fip_addr));
5677 auto fcs_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fcs_addr);
5678 auto fdp_ast = this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword, this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fdp_addr));
5679 auto fds_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fds_addr);
5680 auto mxcsr_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, mxcsr_addr);
5681 auto mxcsr_mask_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, mxcsr_mask_addr);
5682 auto st0_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st0_addr);
5683 auto st1_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st1_addr);
5684 auto st2_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st2_addr);
5685 auto st3_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st3_addr);
5686 auto st4_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st4_addr);
5687 auto st5_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st5_addr);
5688 auto st6_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st6_addr);
5689 auto st7_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st7_addr);
5690 auto xmm0_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm0_addr);
5691 auto xmm1_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm1_addr);
5692 auto xmm2_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm2_addr);
5693 auto xmm3_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm3_addr);
5694 auto xmm4_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm4_addr);
5695 auto xmm5_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm5_addr);
5696 auto xmm6_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm6_addr);
5697 auto xmm7_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm7_addr);
5698 auto ffxsr_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ffxsr);
5699 auto cs_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, cs);
5700
5701 /* Fetch the original values for the XMM0-XMM7 registers */
5702 auto xmm0_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm0);
5703 auto xmm1_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm1);
5704 auto xmm2_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm2);
5705 auto xmm3_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm3);
5706 auto xmm4_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm4);
5707 auto xmm5_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm5);
5708 auto xmm6_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm6);
5709 auto xmm7_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm7);
5710
5711 /* Check if we are running in CPL = 0 (ring 0) and if the FFXSR bit is set in EFER */
5712 auto cpl = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(1, 0, cs_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(0, 2));
5713 auto ffx = this->astCtxt->equal(ffxsr_ast, this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
5714 auto b64 = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->bv(is64bits, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
5715 auto is_fast = this->astCtxt->land(this->astCtxt->land(cpl, ffx), b64);
5716
5717 /* Apply the fast restore logic if needed */
5718 xmm0_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm0_orig, xmm0_ast);
5719 xmm1_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm1_orig, xmm1_ast);
5720 xmm2_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm2_orig, xmm2_ast);
5721 xmm3_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm3_orig, xmm3_ast);
5722 xmm4_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm4_orig, xmm4_ast);
5723 xmm5_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm5_orig, xmm5_ast);
5724 xmm6_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm6_orig, xmm6_ast);
5725 xmm7_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm7_orig, xmm7_ast);
5726
5727 /* Fetch the abridged x87 FPU Tag Word Encoded Bits */
5728 auto eb_1_0 = this->astCtxt->extract(0, 0, ftw_ast);
5729 auto eb_3_2 = this->astCtxt->extract(1, 1, ftw_ast);
5730 auto eb_5_4 = this->astCtxt->extract(2, 2, ftw_ast);
5731 auto eb_7_6 = this->astCtxt->extract(3, 3, ftw_ast);
5732 auto eb_9_8 = this->astCtxt->extract(4, 4, ftw_ast);
5733 auto eb_11_10 = this->astCtxt->extract(5, 5, ftw_ast);
5734 auto eb_13_12 = this->astCtxt->extract(6, 6, ftw_ast);
5735 auto eb_15_14 = this->astCtxt->extract(7, 7, ftw_ast);
5736
5737 /* Extract the fraction from the STX registers */
5738 auto fraction_st0 = this->astCtxt->extract(62, 0, st0_ast);
5739 auto fraction_st1 = this->astCtxt->extract(62, 0, st1_ast);
5740 auto fraction_st2 = this->astCtxt->extract(62, 0, st2_ast);
5741 auto fraction_st3 = this->astCtxt->extract(62, 0, st3_ast);
5742 auto fraction_st4 = this->astCtxt->extract(62, 0, st4_ast);
5743 auto fraction_st5 = this->astCtxt->extract(62, 0, st5_ast);
5744 auto fraction_st6 = this->astCtxt->extract(62, 0, st6_ast);
5745 auto fraction_st7 = this->astCtxt->extract(62, 0, st7_ast);
5746
5747 /* Extract the integer bit from the STX registers */
5748 auto integer_st0 = this->astCtxt->extract(63, 63, st0_ast);
5749 auto integer_st1 = this->astCtxt->extract(63, 63, st1_ast);
5750 auto integer_st2 = this->astCtxt->extract(63, 63, st2_ast);
5751 auto integer_st3 = this->astCtxt->extract(63, 63, st3_ast);
5752 auto integer_st4 = this->astCtxt->extract(63, 63, st4_ast);
5753 auto integer_st5 = this->astCtxt->extract(63, 63, st5_ast);
5754 auto integer_st6 = this->astCtxt->extract(63, 63, st6_ast);
5755 auto integer_st7 = this->astCtxt->extract(63, 63, st7_ast);
5756
5757 /* Extract the exponent from the STX registers */
5758 auto exponent_st0 = this->astCtxt->extract(79, 64, st0_ast);
5759 auto exponent_st1 = this->astCtxt->extract(79, 64, st1_ast);
5760 auto exponent_st2 = this->astCtxt->extract(79, 64, st2_ast);
5761 auto exponent_st3 = this->astCtxt->extract(79, 64, st3_ast);
5762 auto exponent_st4 = this->astCtxt->extract(79, 64, st4_ast);
5763 auto exponent_st5 = this->astCtxt->extract(79, 64, st5_ast);
5764 auto exponent_st6 = this->astCtxt->extract(79, 64, st6_ast);
5765 auto exponent_st7 = this->astCtxt->extract(79, 64, st7_ast);
5766
5767 /* Exponent All Zeros */
5768 auto ea0_st0 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st0, this->astCtxt->bv(0x0000, 16));
5769 auto ea0_st1 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st1, this->astCtxt->bv(0x0000, 16));
5770 auto ea0_st2 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st2, this->astCtxt->bv(0x0000, 16));
5771 auto ea0_st3 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st3, this->astCtxt->bv(0x0000, 16));
5772 auto ea0_st4 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st4, this->astCtxt->bv(0x0000, 16));
5773 auto ea0_st5 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st5, this->astCtxt->bv(0x0000, 16));
5774 auto ea0_st6 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st6, this->astCtxt->bv(0x0000, 16));
5775 auto ea0_st7 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st7, this->astCtxt->bv(0x0000, 16));
5776
5777 /* Exponent All Ones */
5778 auto ea1_st0 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st0, this->astCtxt->bv(0xFFFF, 16));
5779 auto ea1_st1 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st1, this->astCtxt->bv(0xFFFF, 16));
5780 auto ea1_st2 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st2, this->astCtxt->bv(0xFFFF, 16));
5781 auto ea1_st3 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st3, this->astCtxt->bv(0xFFFF, 16));
5782 auto ea1_st4 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st4, this->astCtxt->bv(0xFFFF, 16));
5783 auto ea1_st5 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st5, this->astCtxt->bv(0xFFFF, 16));
5784 auto ea1_st6 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st6, this->astCtxt->bv(0xFFFF, 16));
5785 auto ea1_st7 = this->astCtxt->equal(exponent_st7, this->astCtxt->bv(0xFFFF, 16));
5786
5787 /* Exponent Neither All Zeroes Or Ones */
5788 auto ena01_st0 = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->lor(ea0_st0, ea1_st0), this->astCtxt->bvfalse());
5789 auto ena01_st1 = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->lor(ea0_st1, ea1_st1), this->astCtxt->bvfalse());
5790 auto ena01_st2 = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->lor(ea0_st2, ea1_st2), this->astCtxt->bvfalse());
5791 auto ena01_st3 = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->lor(ea0_st3, ea1_st3), this->astCtxt->bvfalse());
5792 auto ena01_st4 = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->lor(ea0_st4, ea1_st4), this->astCtxt->bvfalse());
5793 auto ena01_st5 = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->lor(ea0_st5, ea1_st5), this->astCtxt->bvfalse());
5794 auto ena01_st6 = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->lor(ea0_st6, ea1_st6), this->astCtxt->bvfalse());
5795 auto ena01_st7 = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->lor(ea0_st7, ea1_st7), this->astCtxt->bvfalse());
5796
5797 /* Integer Bit 0 */
5798 auto ib0_st0 = this->astCtxt->equal(integer_st0, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1));
5799 auto ib0_st1 = this->astCtxt->equal(integer_st1, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1));
5800 auto ib0_st2 = this->astCtxt->equal(integer_st2, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1));
5801 auto ib0_st3 = this->astCtxt->equal(integer_st3, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1));
5802 auto ib0_st4 = this->astCtxt->equal(integer_st4, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1));
5803 auto ib0_st5 = this->astCtxt->equal(integer_st5, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1));
5804 auto ib0_st6 = this->astCtxt->equal(integer_st6, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1));
5805 auto ib0_st7 = this->astCtxt->equal(integer_st7, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1));
5806
5807 /* Fraction All Zeroes */
5808 auto fa0_st0 = this->astCtxt->equal(fraction_st0, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 63));
5809 auto fa0_st1 = this->astCtxt->equal(fraction_st1, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 63));
5810 auto fa0_st2 = this->astCtxt->equal(fraction_st2, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 63));
5811 auto fa0_st3 = this->astCtxt->equal(fraction_st3, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 63));
5812 auto fa0_st4 = this->astCtxt->equal(fraction_st4, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 63));
5813 auto fa0_st5 = this->astCtxt->equal(fraction_st5, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 63));
5814 auto fa0_st6 = this->astCtxt->equal(fraction_st6, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 63));
5815 auto fa0_st7 = this->astCtxt->equal(fraction_st7, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 63));
5816
5817 /* Determine the x87 FPU Tag Word (Diagram at page 379 of the AMD Architecture Programmer's Manual, Volume 2: System Programming) */
5818 auto db_1_0 = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(eb_1_0, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1)),
5819 this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2), // Encoded x87 FPU Tag Bit = 0
5820 this->astCtxt->ite(ea0_st0,
5821 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st0,
5822 this->astCtxt->ite(fa0_st0,
5823 this->astCtxt->bv(1, 2), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction All 0'
5824 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction Not All 0'
5825 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5826 this->astCtxt->ite(ena01_st0,
5827 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st0,
5828 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 0'
5829 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 2)), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5830 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)))); // 'Exponent All 1'
5831
5832 auto db_3_2 = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(eb_3_2, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1)),
5833 this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2), // Encoded x87 FPU Tag Bit = 0
5834 this->astCtxt->ite(ea0_st1,
5835 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st1,
5836 this->astCtxt->ite(fa0_st1,
5837 this->astCtxt->bv(1, 2), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction All 0'
5838 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction Not All 0'
5839 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5840 this->astCtxt->ite(ena01_st1,
5841 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st1,
5842 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 0'
5843 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 2)), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5844 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)))); // 'Exponent All 1'
5845
5846 auto db_5_4 = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(eb_5_4, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1)),
5847 this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2), // Encoded x87 FPU Tag Bit = 0
5848 this->astCtxt->ite(ea0_st2,
5849 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st2,
5850 this->astCtxt->ite(fa0_st2,
5851 this->astCtxt->bv(1, 2), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction All 0'
5852 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction Not All 0'
5853 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5854 this->astCtxt->ite(ena01_st2,
5855 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st2,
5856 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 0'
5857 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 2)), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5858 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)))); // 'Exponent All 1'
5859
5860 auto db_7_6 = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(eb_7_6, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1)),
5861 this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2), // Encoded x87 FPU Tag Bit = 0
5862 this->astCtxt->ite(ea0_st3,
5863 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st3,
5864 this->astCtxt->ite(fa0_st3,
5865 this->astCtxt->bv(1, 2), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction All 0'
5866 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction Not All 0'
5867 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5868 this->astCtxt->ite(ena01_st3,
5869 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st3,
5870 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 0'
5871 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 2)), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5872 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)))); // 'Exponent All 1'
5873
5874 auto db_9_8 = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(eb_9_8, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1)),
5875 this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2), // Encoded x87 FPU Tag Bit = 0
5876 this->astCtxt->ite(ea0_st4,
5877 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st4,
5878 this->astCtxt->ite(fa0_st4,
5879 this->astCtxt->bv(1, 2), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction All 0'
5880 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction Not All 0'
5881 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5882 this->astCtxt->ite(ena01_st4,
5883 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st4,
5884 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 0'
5885 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 2)), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5886 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)))); // 'Exponent All 1'
5887
5888 auto db_11_10 = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(eb_11_10, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1)),
5889 this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2), // Encoded x87 FPU Tag Bit = 0
5890 this->astCtxt->ite(ea0_st5,
5891 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st5,
5892 this->astCtxt->ite(fa0_st5,
5893 this->astCtxt->bv(1, 2), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction All 0'
5894 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction Not All 0'
5895 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5896 this->astCtxt->ite(ena01_st5,
5897 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st5,
5898 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 0'
5899 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 2)), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5900 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)))); // 'Exponent All 1'
5901
5902 auto db_13_12 = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(eb_13_12, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1)),
5903 this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2), // Encoded x87 FPU Tag Bit = 0
5904 this->astCtxt->ite(ea0_st6,
5905 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st6,
5906 this->astCtxt->ite(fa0_st6,
5907 this->astCtxt->bv(1, 2), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction All 0'
5908 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction Not All 0'
5909 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5910 this->astCtxt->ite(ena01_st6,
5911 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st6,
5912 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 0'
5913 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 2)), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5914 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)))); // 'Exponent All 1'
5915
5916 auto db_15_14 = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(eb_15_14, this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1)),
5917 this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2), // Encoded x87 FPU Tag Bit = 0
5918 this->astCtxt->ite(ea0_st7,
5919 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st7,
5920 this->astCtxt->ite(fa0_st7,
5921 this->astCtxt->bv(1, 2), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction All 0'
5922 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 0' + 'Fraction Not All 0'
5923 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)), // 'Exponent All 0' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5924 this->astCtxt->ite(ena01_st7,
5925 this->astCtxt->ite(ib0_st7,
5926 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 0'
5927 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 2)), // 'Exponent Not All 0/1' + 'Integer Bit 1'
5928 this->astCtxt->bv(2, 2)))); // 'Exponent All 1'
5929
5930 /* Restore the x87 FPU Tag Word */
5931 auto uftw_ast = this->astCtxt->concat(db_15_14,
5932 this->astCtxt->concat(db_13_12,
5933 this->astCtxt->concat(db_11_10,
5934 this->astCtxt->concat(db_9_8,
5935 this->astCtxt->concat(db_7_6,
5936 this->astCtxt->concat(db_5_4,
5937 this->astCtxt->concat(db_3_2, db_1_0)))))));
5938
5939 /* Craft the symbolic expressions */
5940 auto fcw_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fcw_ast, fcw, "FXRSTOR FCW operation");
5941 auto fsw_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fsw_ast, fsw, "FXRSTOR FSW operation");
5942 auto ftw_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, uftw_ast, ftw, "FXRSTOR Updated FTW operation");
5943 auto fop_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fop_ast, fop, "FXRSTOR FOP operation");
5944 auto fip_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fip_ast, fip, "FXRSTOR FIP operation");
5945 auto fcs_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fcs_ast, fcs, "FXRSTOR FCS operation");
5946 auto fdp_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fdp_ast, fdp, "FXRSTOR FDP operation");
5947 auto fds_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fds_ast, fds, "FXRSTOR FDS operation");
5948 auto mxcsr_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, mxcsr_ast, mxcsr, "FXRSTOR MXCSR operation");
5949 auto mxcsr_mask_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, mxcsr_mask_ast, mxcsr_mask, "FXRSTOR MXCSR_MASK operation");
5950 auto st0_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st0_ast, st0, "FXRSTOR ST0 operation");
5951 auto st1_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st1_ast, st1, "FXRSTOR ST1 operation");
5952 auto st2_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st2_ast, st2, "FXRSTOR ST2 operation");
5953 auto st3_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st3_ast, st3, "FXRSTOR ST3 operation");
5954 auto st4_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st4_ast, st4, "FXRSTOR ST4 operation");
5955 auto st5_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st5_ast, st5, "FXRSTOR ST5 operation");
5956 auto st6_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st6_ast, st6, "FXRSTOR ST6 operation");
5957 auto st7_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st7_ast, st7, "FXRSTOR ST7 operation");
5958 auto xmm0_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm0_ast, xmm0, "FXRSTOR XMM0 operation");
5959 auto xmm1_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm1_ast, xmm1, "FXRSTOR XMM1 operation");
5960 auto xmm2_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm2_ast, xmm2, "FXRSTOR XMM2 operation");
5961 auto xmm3_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm3_ast, xmm3, "FXRSTOR XMM3 operation");
5962 auto xmm4_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm4_ast, xmm4, "FXRSTOR XMM4 operation");
5963 auto xmm5_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm5_ast, xmm5, "FXRSTOR XMM5 operation");
5964 auto xmm6_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm6_ast, xmm6, "FXRSTOR XMM6 operation");
5965 auto xmm7_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm7_ast, xmm7, "FXRSTOR XMM7 operation");
5966
5967 /* Spread the taint */
5968 fcw_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fcw, fcw_addr);
5969 fsw_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fsw, fsw_addr);
5970 ftw_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(ftw, ftw_addr);
5971 fop_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fop, fop_addr);
5972 fip_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fip, fip_addr);
5973 fcs_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fcs, fcs_addr);
5974 fdp_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fdp, fdp_addr);
5975 fds_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fds, fds_addr);
5976 mxcsr_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(mxcsr, mxcsr_addr);
5977 mxcsr_mask_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(mxcsr_mask, mxcsr_mask_addr);
5978 st0_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st0, st0_addr);
5979 st1_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st1, st1_addr);
5980 st2_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st2, st2_addr);
5981 st3_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st3, st3_addr);
5982 st4_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st4, st4_addr);
5983 st5_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st5, st5_addr);
5984 st6_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st6, st6_addr);
5985 st7_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st7, st7_addr);
5986 xmm0_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm0, xmm0_addr);
5987 xmm1_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm1, xmm1_addr);
5988 xmm2_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm2, xmm2_addr);
5989 xmm3_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm3, xmm3_addr);
5990 xmm4_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm4, xmm4_addr);
5991 xmm5_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm5, xmm5_addr);
5992 xmm6_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm6, xmm6_addr);
5993 xmm7_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm7, xmm7_addr);
5994
5995 /* Additional semantics, symbolic expressions and tainting for the '64-bit Mode Layout (with REX.W = 0)' */
5996 if (is64bits) {
5997 auto xmm8 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM8));
5998 auto xmm9 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM9));
5999 auto xmm10 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM10));
6000 auto xmm11 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM11));
6001 auto xmm12 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM12));
6002 auto xmm13 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM13));
6003 auto xmm14 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM14));
6004 auto xmm15 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM15));
6005
6006 auto xmm8_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 288, xmm8.getSize()));
6007 auto xmm9_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 304, xmm9.getSize()));
6008 auto xmm10_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 320, xmm10.getSize()));
6009 auto xmm11_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 336, xmm11.getSize()));
6010 auto xmm12_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 352, xmm12.getSize()));
6011 auto xmm13_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 368, xmm13.getSize()));
6012 auto xmm14_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 384, xmm14.getSize()));
6013 auto xmm15_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 400, xmm15.getSize()));
6014
6015 auto xmm8_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm8_addr);
6016 auto xmm9_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm9_addr);
6017 auto xmm10_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm10_addr);
6018 auto xmm11_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm11_addr);
6019 auto xmm12_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm12_addr);
6020 auto xmm13_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm13_addr);
6021 auto xmm14_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm14_addr);
6022 auto xmm15_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm15_addr);
6023
6024 /* Fetch the original values for the XMM8-XMM15 registers */
6025 auto xmm8_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm8);
6026 auto xmm9_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm9);
6027 auto xmm10_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm10);
6028 auto xmm11_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm11);
6029 auto xmm12_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm12);
6030 auto xmm13_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm13);
6031 auto xmm14_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm14);
6032 auto xmm15_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm15);
6033
6034 /* Apply the fast restore logic if needed */
6035 xmm8_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm8_orig, xmm8_ast);
6036 xmm9_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm9_orig, xmm9_ast);
6037 xmm10_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm10_orig, xmm10_ast);
6038 xmm11_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm11_orig, xmm11_ast);
6039 xmm12_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm12_orig, xmm12_ast);
6040 xmm13_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm13_orig, xmm13_ast);
6041 xmm14_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm14_orig, xmm14_ast);
6042 xmm15_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm15_orig, xmm15_ast);
6043
6044 auto xmm8_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm8_ast, xmm8, "FXRSTOR XMM8 operation");
6045 auto xmm9_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm9_ast, xmm9, "FXRSTOR XMM9 operation");
6046 auto xmm10_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm10_ast, xmm10, "FXRSTOR XMM10 operation");
6047 auto xmm11_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm11_ast, xmm11, "FXRSTOR XMM11 operation");
6048 auto xmm12_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm12_ast, xmm12, "FXRSTOR XMM12 operation");
6049 auto xmm13_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm13_ast, xmm13, "FXRSTOR XMM13 operation");
6050 auto xmm14_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm14_ast, xmm14, "FXRSTOR XMM14 operation");
6051 auto xmm15_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm15_ast, xmm15, "FXRSTOR XMM15 operation");
6052
6053 xmm8_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm8, xmm8_addr);
6054 xmm9_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm9, xmm9_addr);
6055 xmm10_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm10, xmm10_addr);
6056 xmm11_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm11, xmm11_addr);
6057 xmm12_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm12, xmm12_addr);
6058 xmm13_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm13, xmm13_addr);
6059 xmm14_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm14, xmm14_addr);
6060 xmm15_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm15, xmm15_addr);
6061 }
6062
6063 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
6064 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
6065 }
6066
6067
6068 void x86Semantics::fxrstor64_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
6069 /* Fetch the memory operand */
6070 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
6071 auto& mem = dst.getMemory();
6072 auto m512byte = mem.getAddress();
6073
6074 /* Check if the address is on a 16-byte boundary */
6075 if (m512byte & 0xF) {
6076 this->exception = triton::arch::FAULT_GP;
6077 return;
6078 }
6079
6080 /* Fetch the FPU, STX, SSE, EFER and CS implicit operands */
6081 auto fcw = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FCW));
6082 auto fsw = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FSW));
6083 auto ftw = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FTW));
6084 auto fop = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FOP));
6085 auto fip = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FIP));
6086 auto fcs = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FCS));
6087 auto fdp = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FDP));
6088 auto fds = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FDS));
6089 auto mxcsr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_MXCSR));
6090 auto mxcsr_mask = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_MXCSR_MASK));
6091 auto st0 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST0));
6092 auto st1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST1));
6093 auto st2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST2));
6094 auto st3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST3));
6095 auto st4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST4));
6096 auto st5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST5));
6097 auto st6 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST6));
6098 auto st7 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST7));
6099 auto xmm0 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM0));
6100 auto xmm1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM1));
6101 auto xmm2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM2));
6102 auto xmm3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM3));
6103 auto xmm4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM4));
6104 auto xmm5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM5));
6105 auto xmm6 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM6));
6106 auto xmm7 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM7));
6107 auto xmm8 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM8));
6108 auto xmm9 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM9));
6109 auto xmm10 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM10));
6110 auto xmm11 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM11));
6111 auto xmm12 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM12));
6112 auto xmm13 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM13));
6113 auto xmm14 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM14));
6114 auto xmm15 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM15));
6115 auto ffxsr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EFER_FFXSR));
6116 auto cs = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_CS));
6117
6118 /* Fetch the implicit memory slots for the '64-bit Mode Layout (with REX.W = 1)' */
6119 auto fcw_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 0, fcw.getSize()));
6120 auto fsw_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 2, fsw.getSize()));
6121 auto ftw_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 4, ftw.getSize() / 2));
6122 auto fop_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 6, fop.getSize()));
6123 auto fip_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 8, fip.getSize()));
6124 auto fcs_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 12, fcs.getSize()));
6125 auto fdp_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 16, fdp.getSize()));
6126 auto fds_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 20, fds.getSize()));
6127 auto mxcsr_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 24, mxcsr.getSize()));
6128 auto mxcsr_mask_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 28, mxcsr_mask.getSize()));
6129 auto st0_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 32, st0.getSize()));
6130 auto st1_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 48, st1.getSize()));
6131 auto st2_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 64, st2.getSize()));
6132 auto st3_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 80, st3.getSize()));
6133 auto st4_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 96, st4.getSize()));
6134 auto st5_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 112, st5.getSize()));
6135 auto st6_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 128, st6.getSize()));
6136 auto st7_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 144, st7.getSize()));
6137 auto xmm0_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 160, xmm0.getSize()));
6138 auto xmm1_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 176, xmm1.getSize()));
6139 auto xmm2_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 192, xmm2.getSize()));
6140 auto xmm3_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 208, xmm3.getSize()));
6141 auto xmm4_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 224, xmm4.getSize()));
6142 auto xmm5_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 240, xmm5.getSize()));
6143 auto xmm6_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 256, xmm6.getSize()));
6144 auto xmm7_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 272, xmm7.getSize()));
6145 auto xmm8_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 288, xmm8.getSize()));
6146 auto xmm9_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 304, xmm9.getSize()));
6147 auto xmm10_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 320, xmm10.getSize()));
6148 auto xmm11_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 336, xmm11.getSize()));
6149 auto xmm12_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 352, xmm12.getSize()));
6150 auto xmm13_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 368, xmm13.getSize()));
6151 auto xmm14_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 384, xmm14.getSize()));
6152 auto xmm15_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 400, xmm15.getSize()));
6153
6154 /* Create the symbolic operands */
6155 auto fcw_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fcw_addr);
6156 auto fsw_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fsw_addr);
6157 auto ftw_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ftw_addr);
6158 auto fop_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fop_addr);
6159 auto fip_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fip_addr);
6160 auto fcs_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fcs_addr);
6161 auto fdp_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fdp_addr);
6162 auto fds_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fds_addr);
6163 auto mxcsr_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, mxcsr_addr);
6164 auto mxcsr_mask_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, mxcsr_mask_addr);
6165 auto st0_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st0_addr);
6166 auto st1_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st1_addr);
6167 auto st2_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st2_addr);
6168 auto st3_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st3_addr);
6169 auto st4_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st4_addr);
6170 auto st5_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st5_addr);
6171 auto st6_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st6_addr);
6172 auto st7_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st7_addr);
6173 auto xmm0_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm0_addr);
6174 auto xmm1_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm1_addr);
6175 auto xmm2_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm2_addr);
6176 auto xmm3_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm3_addr);
6177 auto xmm4_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm4_addr);
6178 auto xmm5_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm5_addr);
6179 auto xmm6_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm6_addr);
6180 auto xmm7_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm7_addr);
6181 auto xmm8_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm8_addr);
6182 auto xmm9_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm9_addr);
6183 auto xmm10_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm10_addr);
6184 auto xmm11_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm11_addr);
6185 auto xmm12_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm12_addr);
6186 auto xmm13_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm13_addr);
6187 auto xmm14_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm14_addr);
6188 auto xmm15_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm15_addr);
6189 auto ffxsr_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ffxsr);
6190 auto cs_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, cs);
6191
6192 /* Fetch the original values for the XMM0-XMM15 registers */
6193 auto xmm0_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm0);
6194 auto xmm1_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm1);
6195 auto xmm2_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm2);
6196 auto xmm3_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm3);
6197 auto xmm4_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm4);
6198 auto xmm5_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm5);
