6475 auto xmm11_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm11_ast, xmm11, "FXRSTOR64 XMM11 operation");
6476 auto xmm12_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm12_ast, xmm12, "FXRSTOR64 XMM12 operation");
6477 auto xmm13_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm13_ast, xmm13, "FXRSTOR64 XMM13 operation");
6478 auto xmm14_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm14_ast, xmm14, "FXRSTOR64 XMM14 operation");
6479 auto xmm15_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm15_ast, xmm15, "FXRSTOR64 XMM15 operation");
6480
6481 /* Spread the taint */
6482 fcw_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fcw, fcw_addr);
6483 fsw_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fsw, fsw_addr);
6484 ftw_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(ftw, ftw_addr);
6485 fop_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fop, fop_addr);
6486 fip_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fip, fip_addr);
6487 fcs_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fcs, fcs_addr);
6488 fdp_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fdp, fdp_addr);
6489 fds_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fds, fds_addr);
6490 mxcsr_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(mxcsr, mxcsr_addr);
6491 mxcsr_mask_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(mxcsr_mask, mxcsr_mask_addr);
6492 st0_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st0, st0_addr);
6493 st1_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st1, st1_addr);
6494 st2_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st2, st2_addr);
6495 st3_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st3, st3_addr);
6496 st4_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st4, st4_addr);
6497 st5_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st5, st5_addr);
6498 st6_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st6, st6_addr);
6499 st7_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st7, st7_addr);
6500 xmm0_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm0, xmm0_addr);
6501 xmm1_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm1, xmm1_addr);
6502 xmm2_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm2, xmm2_addr);
6503 xmm3_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm3, xmm3_addr);
6504 xmm4_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm4, xmm4_addr);
6505 xmm5_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm5, xmm5_addr);
6506 xmm6_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm6, xmm6_addr);
6507 xmm7_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm7, xmm7_addr);
6508 xmm8_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm8, xmm8_addr);
6509 xmm9_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm9, xmm9_addr);
6510 xmm10_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm10, xmm10_addr);
6511 xmm11_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm11, xmm11_addr);
6512 xmm12_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm12, xmm12_addr);
6513 xmm13_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm13, xmm13_addr);
6514 xmm14_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm14, xmm14_addr);
6515 xmm15_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm15, xmm15_addr);
6516
6517 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
6518 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
6519 }
6520
6521
6522 void x86Semantics::fxsave_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
6523 /* Fetch the current architecture */
6524 auto arch = this->architecture->getArchitecture();
6525
6526 /* Determine if we are executing in 64 bit mode */
6527 auto is64bits = arch == triton::arch::architecture_e::ARCH_X86_64;
6528
6529 /* Fetch the memory operand */
6530 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
6531 auto& mem = dst.getMemory();
6532 auto m512byte = mem.getAddress();
6533
6534 /* Check if the address is on a 16-byte boundary */
6535 if (m512byte & 0xF) {
6536 this->exception = triton::arch::FAULT_GP;
6537 return;
6538 }
6539
6540 /* Fetch the FPU, STX, SSE, EFER and CS implicit operands */
6541 auto fcw = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FCW));
6542 auto fsw = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FSW));
6543 auto ftw = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FTW));
6544 auto fop = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FOP));
6545 auto fip = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FIP));
6546 auto fcs = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FCS));
6547 auto fdp = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FDP));
6548 auto fds = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FDS));
6549 auto mxcsr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_MXCSR));
6550 auto mxcsr_mask = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_MXCSR_MASK));
6551 auto st0 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST0));
6552 auto st1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST1));
6553 auto st2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST2));
6554 auto st3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST3));
6555 auto st4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST4));
6556 auto st5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST5));
6557 auto st6 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST6));
6558 auto st7 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST7));
6559 auto xmm0 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM0));
6560 auto xmm1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM1));
6561 auto xmm2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM2));
6562 auto xmm3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM3));
6563 auto xmm4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM4));
6564 auto xmm5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM5));
6565 auto xmm6 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM6));
6566 auto xmm7 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM7));
6567 auto ffxsr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EFER_FFXSR));
6568 auto cs = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_CS));
6569
6570 /* Create the symbolic operands */
6571 auto fcw_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fcw);
6572 auto fsw_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fsw);
6573 auto ftw_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ftw);
6574 auto fop_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fop);
6575 auto fip_ast = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dword - 1, 0, this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fip));
6576 auto fcs_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fcs);
6577 auto fdp_ast = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dword - 1, 0, this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fdp));
6578 auto fds_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fds);
6579 auto mxcsr_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, mxcsr);
6580 auto mxcsr_mask_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, mxcsr_mask);
6581 auto st0_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st0);
6582 auto st1_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st1);
6583 auto st2_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st2);
6584 auto st3_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st3);
6585 auto st4_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st4);
6586 auto st5_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st5);
6587 auto st6_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st6);
6588 auto st7_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st7);
6589 auto xmm0_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm0);
6590 auto xmm1_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm1);
6591 auto xmm2_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm2);
6592 auto xmm3_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm3);
6593 auto xmm4_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm4);
6594 auto xmm5_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm5);
6595 auto xmm6_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm6);
6596 auto xmm7_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm7);
6597 auto ffxsr_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ffxsr);
6598 auto cs_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, cs);
6599
6600 /*
6601 Calculate the abridged x87 FPU Tag Word (from 2 bytes to 1 byte encoding)
6602 - Two-bit values of 00, 01, and 10 are encoded as a 1
6603 - A two-bit value of 11 is encoded as a 0
6604 */
6605 auto eb_1_0 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6606 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(1, 0, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6607 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6608
6609 auto eb_3_2 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6610 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(3, 2, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6611 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6612
6613 auto eb_5_4 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6614 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(5, 4, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6615 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6616
6617 auto eb_7_6 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6618 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(7, 6, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6619 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6620
6621 auto eb_9_8 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6622 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(9, 8, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6623 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6624
6625 auto eb_11_10 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6626 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(11, 10, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6627 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6628
6629 auto eb_13_12 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6630 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(13, 12, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6631 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6632
6633 auto eb_15_14 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6634 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(15, 14, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6635 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6636
6637 auto aftw_ast = this->astCtxt->concat(eb_15_14,
6638 this->astCtxt->concat(eb_13_12,
6639 this->astCtxt->concat(eb_11_10,
6640 this->astCtxt->concat(eb_9_8,
6641 this->astCtxt->concat(eb_7_6,
6642 this->astCtxt->concat(eb_5_4,
6643 this->astCtxt->concat(eb_3_2, eb_1_0)))))));
6644
6645 /* Fetch the implicit memory slots for the 'Non-64-bit Mode Layout' */
6646 auto fcw_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 0, fcw.getSize()));
6647 auto fsw_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 2, fsw.getSize()));
6648 auto ftw_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 4, ftw.getSize() / 2));
6649 auto fop_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 6, fop.getSize()));
6650 auto fip_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 8, fip.getSize() / 2));
6651 auto fcs_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 12, fcs.getSize()));
6652 auto fdp_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 16, fdp.getSize() / 2));
6653 auto fds_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 20, fds.getSize()));
6654 auto mxcsr_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 24, mxcsr.getSize()));
6655 auto mxcsr_mask_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 28, mxcsr_mask.getSize()));
6656 auto st0_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 32, st0.getSize()));
6657 auto st1_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 48, st1.getSize()));
6658 auto st2_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 64, st2.getSize()));
6659 auto st3_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 80, st3.getSize()));
6660 auto st4_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 96, st4.getSize()));
6661 auto st5_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 112, st5.getSize()));
6662 auto st6_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 128, st6.getSize()));
6663 auto st7_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 144, st7.getSize()));
6664 auto xmm0_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 160, xmm0.getSize()));
6665 auto xmm1_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 176, xmm1.getSize()));
6666 auto xmm2_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 192, xmm2.getSize()));
6667 auto xmm3_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 208, xmm3.getSize()));
6668 auto xmm4_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 224, xmm4.getSize()));
6669 auto xmm5_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 240, xmm5.getSize()));
6670 auto xmm6_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 256, xmm6.getSize()));
6671 auto xmm7_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 272, xmm7.getSize()));
6672
6673 /* Fetch the original values of the XMM0-XMM7 memory spaces */
6674 auto xmm0_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm0_addr);
6675 auto xmm1_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm1_addr);
6676 auto xmm2_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm2_addr);
6677 auto xmm3_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm3_addr);
6678 auto xmm4_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm4_addr);
6679 auto xmm5_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm5_addr);
6680 auto xmm6_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm6_addr);
6681 auto xmm7_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm7_addr);
6682
6683 /* Check if we are running in CPL = 0 (ring 0) and if the FFXSR bit is set in EFER */
6684 auto cpl = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(1, 0, cs_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(0, 2));
6685 auto ffx = this->astCtxt->equal(ffxsr_ast, this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6686 auto b64 = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->bv(is64bits, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6687 auto is_fast = this->astCtxt->land(this->astCtxt->land(cpl, ffx), b64);
6688
6689 /* Apply the fast save logic if needed */
6690 xmm0_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm0_orig, xmm0_ast);
6691 xmm1_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm1_orig, xmm1_ast);
6692 xmm2_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm2_orig, xmm2_ast);
6693 xmm3_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm3_orig, xmm3_ast);
6694 xmm4_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm4_orig, xmm4_ast);
6695 xmm5_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm5_orig, xmm5_ast);
6696 xmm6_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm6_orig, xmm6_ast);
6697 xmm7_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm7_orig, xmm7_ast);
6698
6699 /* Craft the symbolic expressions */
6700 auto fcw_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fcw_ast, fcw_addr, "FXSAVE FCW operation");
6701 auto fsw_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fsw_ast, fsw_addr, "FXSAVE FSW operation");
6702 auto ftw_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, aftw_ast, ftw_addr, "FXSAVE Abridged FTW operation");
6703 auto fop_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fop_ast, fop_addr, "FXSAVE FOP operation");
6704 auto fip_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fip_ast, fip_addr, "FXSAVE FIP operation");
6705 auto fcs_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fcs_ast, fcs_addr, "FXSAVE FCS operation");
6706 auto fdp_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fdp_ast, fdp_addr, "FXSAVE FDP operation");
6707 auto fds_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fds_ast, fds_addr, "FXSAVE FDS operation");
6708 auto mxcsr_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, mxcsr_ast, mxcsr_addr, "FXSAVE MXCSR operation");
6709 auto mxcsr_mask_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, mxcsr_mask_ast, mxcsr_mask_addr, "FXSAVE MXCSR_MASK operation");
6710 auto st0_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st0_ast, st0_addr, "FXSAVE ST0 operation");
6711 auto st1_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st1_ast, st1_addr, "FXSAVE ST1 operation");
6712 auto st2_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st2_ast, st2_addr, "FXSAVE ST2 operation");
6713 auto st3_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st3_ast, st3_addr, "FXSAVE ST3 operation");
6714 auto st4_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st4_ast, st4_addr, "FXSAVE ST4 operation");
6715 auto st5_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st5_ast, st5_addr, "FXSAVE ST5 operation");
6716 auto st6_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st6_ast, st6_addr, "FXSAVE ST6 operation");
6717 auto st7_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st7_ast, st7_addr, "FXSAVE ST7 operation");
6718 auto xmm0_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm0_ast, xmm0_addr, "FXSAVE XMM0 operation");
6719 auto xmm1_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm1_ast, xmm1_addr, "FXSAVE XMM1 operation");
6720 auto xmm2_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm2_ast, xmm2_addr, "FXSAVE XMM2 operation");
6721 auto xmm3_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm3_ast, xmm3_addr, "FXSAVE XMM3 operation");
6722 auto xmm4_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm4_ast, xmm4_addr, "FXSAVE XMM4 operation");
6723 auto xmm5_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm5_ast, xmm5_addr, "FXSAVE XMM5 operation");
6724 auto xmm6_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm6_ast, xmm6_addr, "FXSAVE XMM6 operation");
6725 auto xmm7_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm7_ast, xmm7_addr, "FXSAVE XMM7 operation");
6726
6727 /* Spread the taint */
6728 fcw_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fcw_addr, fcw);
6729 fsw_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fsw_addr, fsw);
6730 ftw_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(ftw_addr, ftw);
6731 fop_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fop_addr, fop);
6732 fip_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fip_addr, fip);
6733 fcs_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fcs_addr, fcs);
6734 fdp_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fdp_addr, fdp);
6735 fds_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fds_addr, fds);
6736 mxcsr_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(mxcsr_addr, mxcsr);
6737 mxcsr_mask_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(mxcsr_mask_addr, mxcsr_mask);
6738 st0_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st0_addr, st0);
6739 st1_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st1_addr, st1);
6740 st2_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st2_addr, st2);
6741 st3_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st3_addr, st3);
6742 st4_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st4_addr, st4);
6743 st5_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st5_addr, st5);
6744 st6_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st6_addr, st6);
6745 st7_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st7_addr, st7);
6746 xmm0_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm0_addr, xmm0);
6747 xmm1_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm1_addr, xmm1);
6748 xmm2_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm2_addr, xmm2);
6749 xmm3_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm3_addr, xmm3);
6750 xmm4_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm4_addr, xmm4);
6751 xmm5_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm5_addr, xmm5);
6752 xmm6_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm6_addr, xmm6);
6753 xmm7_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm7_addr, xmm7);
6754
6755 /* Additional semantics, symbolic expressions and tainting for the '64-bit Mode Layout (with REX.W = 0)' */
6756 if (is64bits) {
6757 auto xmm8 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM8));
6758 auto xmm9 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM9));
6759 auto xmm10 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM10));
6760 auto xmm11 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM11));
6761 auto xmm12 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM12));
6762 auto xmm13 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM13));
6763 auto xmm14 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM14));
6764 auto xmm15 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM15));
6765
6766 auto xmm8_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm8);
6767 auto xmm9_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm9);
6768 auto xmm10_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm10);
6769 auto xmm11_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm11);
6770 auto xmm12_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm12);
6771 auto xmm13_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm13);
6772 auto xmm14_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm14);
6773 auto xmm15_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm15);
6774
6775 auto xmm8_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 288, xmm8.getSize()));
6776 auto xmm9_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 304, xmm9.getSize()));
6777 auto xmm10_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 320, xmm10.getSize()));
6778 auto xmm11_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 336, xmm11.getSize()));
6779 auto xmm12_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 352, xmm12.getSize()));
6780 auto xmm13_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 368, xmm13.getSize()));
6781 auto xmm14_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 384, xmm14.getSize()));
6782 auto xmm15_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 400, xmm15.getSize()));
6783
6784 /* Fetch the original values of the XMM8-XMM15 memory spaces */
6785 auto xmm8_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm8_addr);
6786 auto xmm9_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm9_addr);
6787 auto xmm10_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm10_addr);
6788 auto xmm11_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm11_addr);
6789 auto xmm12_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm12_addr);
6790 auto xmm13_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm13_addr);
6791 auto xmm14_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm14_addr);
6792 auto xmm15_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm15_addr);
6793
6794 /* Check if we are running in CPL = 0 (ring 0) and if the FFXSR bit is set in EFER */
6795 auto cpl = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(1, 0, cs_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(0, 2));
6796 auto ffx = this->astCtxt->equal(ffxsr_ast, this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6797 auto is_fast = this->astCtxt->land(cpl, ffx);
6798
6799 /* Apply the fast save logic if needed */
6800 xmm8_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm8_orig, xmm8_ast);
6801 xmm9_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm9_orig, xmm9_ast);
6802 xmm10_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm10_orig, xmm10_ast);
6803 xmm11_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm11_orig, xmm11_ast);
6804 xmm12_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm12_orig, xmm12_ast);
6805 xmm13_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm13_orig, xmm13_ast);
6806 xmm14_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm14_orig, xmm14_ast);
6807 xmm15_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm15_orig, xmm15_ast);
6808
6809 auto xmm8_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm8_ast, xmm8_addr, "FXSAVE XMM8 operation");
6810 auto xmm9_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm9_ast, xmm9_addr, "FXSAVE XMM9 operation");
6811 auto xmm10_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm10_ast, xmm10_addr, "FXSAVE XMM10 operation");
6812 auto xmm11_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm11_ast, xmm11_addr, "FXSAVE XMM11 operation");
6813 auto xmm12_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm12_ast, xmm12_addr, "FXSAVE XMM12 operation");
6814 auto xmm13_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm13_ast, xmm13_addr, "FXSAVE XMM13 operation");
6815 auto xmm14_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm14_ast, xmm14_addr, "FXSAVE XMM14 operation");
6816 auto xmm15_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm15_ast, xmm15_addr, "FXSAVE XMM15 operation");
6817
6818 xmm8_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm8_addr, xmm8);
6819 xmm9_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm9_addr, xmm9);
6820 xmm10_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm10_addr, xmm10);
6821 xmm11_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm11_addr, xmm11);
6822 xmm12_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm12_addr, xmm12);
6823 xmm13_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm13_addr, xmm13);
6824 xmm14_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm14_addr, xmm14);
6825 xmm15_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm15_addr, xmm15);
6826 }
6827
6828 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
6829 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
6830 }
6831
6832
6833 void x86Semantics::fxsave64_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
6834 /* Fetch the memory operand */
6835 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
6836 auto& mem = dst.getMemory();
6837 auto m512byte = mem.getAddress();
6838
6839 /* Check if the address is on a 16-byte boundary */
6840 if (m512byte & 0xF) {
6841 this->exception = triton::arch::FAULT_GP;
6842 return;
6843 }
6844
6845 /* Fetch the FPU, STX, SSE, EFER and CS implicit operands */
6846 auto fcw = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FCW));
6847 auto fsw = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FSW));
6848 auto ftw = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FTW));
6849 auto fop = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FOP));
6850 auto fip = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FIP));
6851 auto fcs = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FCS));
6852 auto fdp = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FDP));
6853 auto fds = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_FDS));
6854 auto mxcsr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_MXCSR));
6855 auto mxcsr_mask = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_MXCSR_MASK));
6856 auto st0 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST0));
6857 auto st1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST1));
6858 auto st2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST2));
6859 auto st3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST3));
6860 auto st4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST4));
6861 auto st5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST5));
6862 auto st6 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST6));
6863 auto st7 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ST7));
6864 auto xmm0 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM0));
6865 auto xmm1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM1));
6866 auto xmm2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM2));
6867 auto xmm3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM3));
6868 auto xmm4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM4));
6869 auto xmm5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM5));
6870 auto xmm6 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM6));
6871 auto xmm7 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM7));
6872 auto xmm8 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM8));
6873 auto xmm9 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM9));
6874 auto xmm10 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM10));
6875 auto xmm11 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM11));
6876 auto xmm12 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM12));
6877 auto xmm13 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM13));
6878 auto xmm14 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM14));
6879 auto xmm15 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_XMM15));
6880 auto ffxsr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EFER_FFXSR));
6881 auto cs = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_CS));
6882
6883 /* Create the symbolic operands */
6884 auto fcw_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fcw);
6885 auto fsw_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fsw);
6886 auto ftw_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ftw);
6887 auto fop_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fop);
6888 auto fip_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fip);
6889 auto fcs_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fcs);
6890 auto fdp_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fdp);
6891 auto fds_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, fds);
6892 auto mxcsr_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, mxcsr);
6893 auto mxcsr_mask_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, mxcsr_mask);
6894 auto st0_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st0);
6895 auto st1_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st1);
6896 auto st2_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st2);
6897 auto st3_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st3);
6898 auto st4_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st4);
6899 auto st5_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st5);
6900 auto st6_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st6);
6901 auto st7_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, st7);
6902 auto xmm0_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm0);
6903 auto xmm1_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm1);
6904 auto xmm2_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm2);
6905 auto xmm3_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm3);
6906 auto xmm4_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm4);
6907 auto xmm5_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm5);
6908 auto xmm6_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm6);
6909 auto xmm7_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm7);
6910 auto xmm8_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm8);
6911 auto xmm9_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm9);
6912 auto xmm10_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm10);
6913 auto xmm11_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm11);
6914 auto xmm12_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm12);
6915 auto xmm13_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm13);
6916 auto xmm14_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm14);
6917 auto xmm15_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, xmm15);
6918 auto ffxsr_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ffxsr);
6919 auto cs_ast = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, cs);
6920
6921 /*
6922 Calculate the abridged x87 FPU Tag Word (from 2 bytes to 1 byte encoding)
6923 - Two-bit values of 00, 01, and 10 are encoded as a 1
6924 - A two-bit value of 11 is encoded as a 0
6925 */
6926 auto eb_1_0 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6927 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(1, 0, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6928 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6929
6930 auto eb_3_2 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6931 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(3, 2, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6932 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6933
6934 auto eb_5_4 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6935 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(5, 4, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6936 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6937
6938 auto eb_7_6 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6939 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(7, 6, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6940 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6941
6942 auto eb_9_8 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6943 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(9, 8, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6944 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6945
6946 auto eb_11_10 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6947 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(11, 10, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6948 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6949
6950 auto eb_13_12 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6951 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(13, 12, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6952 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6953
6954 auto eb_15_14 = this->astCtxt->ite(
6955 this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(15, 14, ftw_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(3, 2)),
6956 this->astCtxt->bv(0, 1), this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
6957
6958 auto aftw_ast = this->astCtxt->concat(eb_15_14,
6959 this->astCtxt->concat(eb_13_12,
6960 this->astCtxt->concat(eb_11_10,
6961 this->astCtxt->concat(eb_9_8,
6962 this->astCtxt->concat(eb_7_6,
6963 this->astCtxt->concat(eb_5_4,
6964 this->astCtxt->concat(eb_3_2, eb_1_0)))))));
6965
6966 /* Fetch the implicit memory slots for the '64-bit Mode Layout (with REX.W = 1)' */
6967 auto fcw_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 0, fcw.getSize()));
6968 auto fsw_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 2, fsw.getSize()));
6969 auto ftw_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 4, ftw.getSize() / 2));
6970 auto fop_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 6, fop.getSize()));
6971 auto fip_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 8, fip.getSize()));
6972 auto fcs_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 12, fcs.getSize()));
6973 auto fdp_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 16, fdp.getSize()));
6974 auto fds_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 20, fds.getSize()));
6975 auto mxcsr_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 24, mxcsr.getSize()));
6976 auto mxcsr_mask_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 28, mxcsr_mask.getSize()));
6977 auto st0_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 32, st0.getSize()));
6978 auto st1_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 48, st1.getSize()));
6979 auto st2_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 64, st2.getSize()));
6980 auto st3_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 80, st3.getSize()));
6981 auto st4_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 96, st4.getSize()));
6982 auto st5_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 112, st5.getSize()));
6983 auto st6_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 128, st6.getSize()));
6984 auto st7_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 144, st7.getSize()));
6985 auto xmm0_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 160, xmm0.getSize()));
6986 auto xmm1_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 176, xmm1.getSize()));
6987 auto xmm2_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 192, xmm2.getSize()));
6988 auto xmm3_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 208, xmm3.getSize()));
6989 auto xmm4_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 224, xmm4.getSize()));
6990 auto xmm5_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 240, xmm5.getSize()));
6991 auto xmm6_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 256, xmm6.getSize()));
6992 auto xmm7_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 272, xmm7.getSize()));
6993 auto xmm8_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 288, xmm8.getSize()));
6994 auto xmm9_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 304, xmm9.getSize()));
6995 auto xmm10_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 320, xmm10.getSize()));
6996 auto xmm11_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 336, xmm11.getSize()));
6997 auto xmm12_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 352, xmm12.getSize()));
6998 auto xmm13_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 368, xmm13.getSize()));
6999 auto xmm14_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 384, xmm14.getSize()));
7000 auto xmm15_addr = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(m512byte + 400, xmm15.getSize()));
7001
7002 /* Fetch the original values of the XMM0-XMM7 memory spaces */
7003 auto xmm0_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm0_addr);
7004 auto xmm1_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm1_addr);
7005 auto xmm2_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm2_addr);
7006 auto xmm3_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm3_addr);
7007 auto xmm4_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm4_addr);
7008 auto xmm5_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm5_addr);
7009 auto xmm6_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm6_addr);
7010 auto xmm7_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm7_addr);
7011 auto xmm8_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm8_addr);
7012 auto xmm9_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm9_addr);
7013 auto xmm10_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm10_addr);
7014 auto xmm11_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm11_addr);
7015 auto xmm12_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm12_addr);
7016 auto xmm13_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm13_addr);
7017 auto xmm14_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm14_addr);
7018 auto xmm15_orig = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(xmm15_addr);
7019
7020 /* Check if we are running in CPL = 0 (ring 0) and if the FFXSR bit is set in EFER */
7021 auto cpl = this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(1, 0, cs_ast), this->astCtxt->bv(0, 2));
7022 auto ffx = this->astCtxt->equal(ffxsr_ast, this->astCtxt->bv(1, 1));
7023 auto is_fast = this->astCtxt->land(cpl, ffx);
7024
7025 /* Apply the fast save logic if needed */
7026 xmm0_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm0_orig, xmm0_ast);
7027 xmm1_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm1_orig, xmm1_ast);
7028 xmm2_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm2_orig, xmm2_ast);
7029 xmm3_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm3_orig, xmm3_ast);
7030 xmm4_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm4_orig, xmm4_ast);
7031 xmm5_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm5_orig, xmm5_ast);
7032 xmm6_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm6_orig, xmm6_ast);
7033 xmm7_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm7_orig, xmm7_ast);
7034 xmm8_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm8_orig, xmm8_ast);
7035 xmm9_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm9_orig, xmm9_ast);
7036 xmm10_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm10_orig, xmm10_ast);
7037 xmm11_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm11_orig, xmm11_ast);
7038 xmm12_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm12_orig, xmm12_ast);
7039 xmm13_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm13_orig, xmm13_ast);
7040 xmm14_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm14_orig, xmm14_ast);
7041 xmm15_ast = this->astCtxt->ite(is_fast, xmm15_orig, xmm15_ast);
7042
7043 /* Craft the symbolic expressions */
7044 auto fcw_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fcw_ast, fcw_addr, "FXSAVE64 FCW operation");
7045 auto fsw_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fsw_ast, fsw_addr, "FXSAVE64 FSW operation");
7046 auto ftw_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, aftw_ast, ftw_addr, "FXSAVE64 Abridged FTW operation");
7047 auto fop_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fop_ast, fop_addr, "FXSAVE64 FOP operation");
7048 auto fip_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fip_ast, fip_addr, "FXSAVE64 FIP operation");
7049 auto fcs_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fcs_ast, fcs_addr, "FXSAVE64 FCS operation");
7050 auto fdp_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fdp_ast, fdp_addr, "FXSAVE64 FDP operation");
7051 auto fds_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, fds_ast, fds_addr, "FXSAVE64 FDS operation");
7052 auto mxcsr_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, mxcsr_ast, mxcsr_addr, "FXSAVE64 MXCSR operation");
7053 auto mxcsr_mask_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, mxcsr_mask_ast, mxcsr_mask_addr, "FXSAVE64 MXCSR_MASK operation");
7054 auto st0_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st0_ast, st0_addr, "FXSAVE64 ST0 operation");
7055 auto st1_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st1_ast, st1_addr, "FXSAVE64 ST1 operation");
7056 auto st2_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st2_ast, st2_addr, "FXSAVE64 ST2 operation");
7057 auto st3_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st3_ast, st3_addr, "FXSAVE64 ST3 operation");
7058 auto st4_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st4_ast, st4_addr, "FXSAVE64 ST4 operation");
7059 auto st5_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st5_ast, st5_addr, "FXSAVE64 ST5 operation");
7060 auto st6_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st6_ast, st6_addr, "FXSAVE64 ST6 operation");
7061 auto st7_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, st7_ast, st7_addr, "FXSAVE64 ST7 operation");
7062 auto xmm0_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm0_ast, xmm0_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM0 operation");
7063 auto xmm1_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm1_ast, xmm1_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM1 operation");
7064 auto xmm2_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm2_ast, xmm2_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM2 operation");
7065 auto xmm3_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm3_ast, xmm3_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM3 operation");
7066 auto xmm4_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm4_ast, xmm4_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM4 operation");
7067 auto xmm5_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm5_ast, xmm5_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM5 operation");
7068 auto xmm6_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm6_ast, xmm6_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM6 operation");
7069 auto xmm7_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm7_ast, xmm7_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM7 operation");
7070 auto xmm8_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm8_ast, xmm8_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM8 operation");
7071 auto xmm9_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm9_ast, xmm9_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM9 operation");
7072 auto xmm10_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm10_ast, xmm10_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM10 operation");
7073 auto xmm11_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm11_ast, xmm11_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM11 operation");
7074 auto xmm12_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm12_ast, xmm12_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM12 operation");
7075 auto xmm13_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm13_ast, xmm13_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM13 operation");
7076 auto xmm14_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm14_ast, xmm14_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM14 operation");
7077 auto xmm15_expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, xmm15_ast, xmm15_addr, "FXSAVE64 XMM15 operation");
7078
7079 /* Spread the taint */
7080 fcw_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fcw_addr, fcw);
7081 fsw_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fsw_addr, fsw);
7082 ftw_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(ftw_addr, ftw);
7083 fop_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fop_addr, fop);
7084 fip_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fip_addr, fip);
7085 fcs_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fcs_addr, fcs);
7086 fdp_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fdp_addr, fdp);
7087 fds_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(fds_addr, fds);
7088 mxcsr_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(mxcsr_addr, mxcsr);
7089 mxcsr_mask_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(mxcsr_mask_addr, mxcsr_mask);
7090 st0_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st0_addr, st0);
7091 st1_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st1_addr, st1);
7092 st2_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st2_addr, st2);
7093 st3_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st3_addr, st3);
7094 st4_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st4_addr, st4);
7095 st5_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st5_addr, st5);
7096 st6_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st6_addr, st6);
7097 st7_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(st7_addr, st7);
7098 xmm0_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm0_addr, xmm0);
7099 xmm1_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm1_addr, xmm1);
7100 xmm2_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm2_addr, xmm2);
7101 xmm3_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm3_addr, xmm3);
7102 xmm4_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm4_addr, xmm4);
7103 xmm5_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm5_addr, xmm5);
7104 xmm6_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm6_addr, xmm6);
7105 xmm7_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm7_addr, xmm7);
7106 xmm8_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm8_addr, xmm8);
7107 xmm9_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm9_addr, xmm9);
7108 xmm10_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm10_addr, xmm10);
7109 xmm11_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm11_addr, xmm11);
7110 xmm12_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm12_addr, xmm12);
7111 xmm13_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm13_addr, xmm13);
7112 xmm14_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm14_addr, xmm14);
7113 xmm15_expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(xmm15_addr, xmm15);
7114
7115 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
7116 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
7117 }
7118
7119
7120 void x86Semantics::idiv_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
7121 auto& src = inst.operands[0];
7122
7123 /* Create symbolic operands */
7124 auto divisor = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
7125
7126 /* Return an exception if the divisor is zero */
7127 if (divisor->evaluate() == 0) {
7128 this->exception = triton::arch::FAULT_DE;
7129 return;
7130 }
7131
7132 /* Create symbolic expression */
7133 switch (src.getSize()) {
7134
7135 case triton::size::byte: {
7136 /* AX */
7137 auto ax = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
7138 auto dividend = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ax);
7139 /* res = AX / Source */
7140 auto result = this->astCtxt->bvsdiv(dividend, this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::byte, divisor));
7141 /* mod = AX % Source */
7142 auto mod = this->astCtxt->bvsmod(dividend, this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::byte, divisor));
7143 /* AH = mod */
7144 /* AL = res */
7145 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(
7146 this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::byte - 1), 0, mod), /* AH = mod */
7147 this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::byte - 1), 0, result) /* AL = res */
7148 );
7149 /* Create symbolic expression */
7150 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, ax, "IDIV operation");
7151 /* Apply the taint */
7152 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(ax, src);
7153 break;
7154 }
7155
7156 case triton::size::word: {
7157 /* DX:AX */
7158 auto dx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_DX));
7159 auto ax = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
7160 auto dividend = this->astCtxt->concat(this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dx), this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ax));
7161 /* res = DX:AX / Source */
7162 auto result = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::word - 1), 0, this->astCtxt->bvsdiv(dividend, this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::word, divisor)));
7163 /* mod = DX:AX % Source */
7164 auto mod = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::word - 1), 0, this->astCtxt->bvsmod(dividend, this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::word, divisor)));
7165 /* Create the symbolic expression for AX */
7166 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, result, ax, "IDIV operation");
7167 /* Apply the taint for AX */
7168 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(ax, src);
7169 /* Create the symbolic expression for DX */
7170 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, mod, dx, "IDIV operation");
7171 /* Apply the taint for DX */
7172 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dx, src);
7173 break;
7174 }
7175
7176 case triton::size::dword: {
7177 /* EDX:EAX */
7178 auto edx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EDX));
7179 auto eax = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EAX));
7180 auto dividend = this->astCtxt->concat(this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, edx), this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, eax));
7181 /* res = EDX:EAX / Source */
7182 auto result = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::dword - 1), 0, this->astCtxt->bvsdiv(dividend, this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::dword, divisor)));
7183 /* mod = EDX:EAX % Source */
7184 auto mod = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::dword - 1), 0, this->astCtxt->bvsmod(dividend, this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::dword, divisor)));
7185 /* Create the symbolic expression for EAX */
7186 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, result, eax, "IDIV operation");
7187 /* Apply the taint for EAX */
7188 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(eax, src);
7189 /* Create the symbolic expression for EDX */
7190 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, mod, edx, "IDIV operation");
7191 /* Apply the taint for EDX */
7192 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(edx, src);
7193 break;
7194 }
7195
7196 case triton::size::qword: {
7197 /* RDX:RAX */
7198 auto rdx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RDX));
7199 auto rax = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RAX));
7200 auto dividend = this->astCtxt->concat(this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, rdx), this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, rax));
7201 /* res = RDX:RAX / Source */
7202 auto result = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::qword - 1), 0, this->astCtxt->bvsdiv(dividend, this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::qword, divisor)));
7203 /* mod = RDX:RAX % Source */
7204 auto mod = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::qword - 1), 0, this->astCtxt->bvsmod(dividend, this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::qword, divisor)));
7205 /* Create the symbolic expression for RAX */
7206 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, result, rax, "IDIV operation");
7207 /* Apply the taint for EAX */
7208 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(rax, src);
7209 /* Create the symbolic expression for RDX */
7210 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, mod, rdx, "IDIV operation");
7211 /* Apply the taint for EDX */
7212 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(rdx, src);
7213 break;
7214 }
7215
7216 }
7217
7218 /* Tag undefined flags */
7219 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AF));
7220 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_CF));
7221 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_OF));
7222 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_PF));
7223 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_SF));
7224 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ZF));
7225
7226 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
7227 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
7228 }
7229
7230
7231 void x86Semantics::imul_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
7232 switch (inst.operands.size()) {
7233
7234 /* one operand */
7235 case 1: {
7236 auto& src = inst.operands[0];
7237
7238 /* size of the Operand */
7239 switch (src.getSize()) {
7240
7241 /* dst = AX */
7242 case triton::size::byte: {
7243 auto ax = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
7244 auto al = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AL));
7245 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, al);
7246 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
7247 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvmul(this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::byte, op1), this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::byte, op2));
7248 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, ax, "IMUL operation");
7249 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(ax, src);
7250 this->cfImul_s(inst, expr, al, this->astCtxt->bvmul(op1, op2), node);
7251 this->ofImul_s(inst, expr, al, this->astCtxt->bvmul(op1, op2), node);
7252 break;
7253 }
7254
7255 /* dst = DX:AX */
7256 case triton::size::word: {
7257 auto ax = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
7258 auto dx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_DX));
7259 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, ax);
7260 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
7261 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(op1, op2);
7262 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::word, op1), this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::word, op2));
7263 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, ax, "IMUL operation");
7264 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dword-1, triton::bitsize::word, node2), dx, "IMUL operation");
7265 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(ax, src);
7266 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dx, ax);
7267 this->cfImul_s(inst, expr1, ax, node1, node2);
7268 this->ofImul_s(inst, expr1, ax, node1, node2);
7269 break;
7270 }
7271
7272 /* dst = EDX:EAX */
7273 case triton::size::dword: {
7274 auto eax = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EAX));
7275 auto edx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EDX));
7276 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, eax);
7277 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
7278 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(op1, op2);
7279 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::dword, op1), this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::dword, op2));
7280 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, eax, "IMUL operation");
7281 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::qword-1, triton::bitsize::dword, node2), edx, "IMUL operation");
7282 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(eax, src);
7283 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(edx, eax);
7284 this->cfImul_s(inst, expr1, eax, node1, node2);
7285 this->ofImul_s(inst, expr1, eax, node1, node2);
7286 break;
7287 }
7288
7289 /* dst = RDX:RAX */
7290 case triton::size::qword: {
7291 auto rax = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RAX));
7292 auto rdx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RDX));
7293 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, rax);
7294 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
7295 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(op1, op2);
7296 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::qword, op1), this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::qword, op2));
7297 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, rax, "IMUL operation");
7298 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dqword-1, triton::bitsize::qword, node2), rdx, "IMUL operation");
7299 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(rax, src);
7300 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(rdx, rax);
7301 this->cfImul_s(inst, expr1, rax, node1, node2);
7302 this->ofImul_s(inst, expr1, rax, node1, node2);
7303 break;
7304 }
7305
7306 }
7307 break;
7308 }
7309
7310 /* two operands */
7311 case 2: {
7312 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
7313 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
7314 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
7315 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
7316 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(op1, op2);
7317 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(this->astCtxt->sx(dst.getBitSize(), op1), this->astCtxt->sx(src.getBitSize(), op2));
7318 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, dst, "IMUL operation");
7319 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
7320 this->cfImul_s(inst, expr, dst, node1, node2);
7321 this->ofImul_s(inst, expr, dst, node1, node2);
7322 break;
7323 }
7324
7325 /* three operands */
7326 case 3: {
7327 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
7328 auto& src1 = inst.operands[1];
7329 auto& src2 = inst.operands[2];
7330 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
7331 auto op3 = this->astCtxt->sx(src1.getBitSize() - src2.getBitSize(), this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2));
7332 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(op2, op3);
7333 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(this->astCtxt->sx(src1.getBitSize(), op2), this->astCtxt->sx(src2.getBitSize(), op3));
7334 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, dst, "IMUL operation");
7335 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->setTaint(dst, this->taintEngine->isTainted(src1) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(src2));
7336 this->cfImul_s(inst, expr, dst, node1, node2);
7337 this->ofImul_s(inst, expr, dst, node1, node2);
7338 break;
7339 }
7340
7341 }
7342
7343 /* Tag undefined flags */
7344 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AF));
7345 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_PF));
7346 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_SF));
7347 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ZF));
7348
7349 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
7350 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
7351 }
7352
7353
7354 void x86Semantics::inc_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
7355 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
7356
7357 /* Create symbolic operands */
7358 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
7359 auto op2 = this->astCtxt->bv(1, dst.getBitSize());
7360
7361 /* Create the semantics */
7362 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvadd(op1, op2);
7363
7364 /* Create symbolic expression */
7365 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "INC operation");
7366
7367 /* Spread taint */
7368 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, dst);
7369
7370 /* Update symbolic flags */
7371 this->af_s(inst, expr, dst, op1, op2);
7372 this->ofAdd_s(inst, expr, dst, op1, op2);
7373 this->pf_s(inst, expr, dst);
7374 this->sf_s(inst, expr, dst);
7375 this->zf_s(inst, expr, dst);
7376
7377 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
7378 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
7379 }
7380

7383 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
7384 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
7385 }

7393
7394 void x86Semantics::ja_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
7395 auto pc = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getProgramCounter());
7396 auto cf = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_CF));
7397 auto zf = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ZF));
7398 auto srcImm1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(Immediate(inst.getNextAddress(), pc.getSize()));
7399 auto& srcImm2 = inst.operands[0];
7400
7401 /* Create symbolic operands */
7402 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, cf);
7403 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, zf);
7404 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, srcImm1);
7405 auto op4 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, srcImm2);
7406
7407 /* Create the semantics */
7408 auto node = this->astCtxt->ite(
7409 this->astCtxt->equal(
7410 this->astCtxt->bvand(
7411 this->astCtxt->bvnot(op1),
7412 this->astCtxt->bvnot(op2)
7413 ),
7414 this->astCtxt->bvtrue()
7415 ), op4, op3);
7416
7417 /* Create symbolic expression */
7418 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, pc, "Program Counter");
7419
7420 /* Set condition flag */
7421 if (op1->evaluate().is_zero() && op2->evaluate().is_zero())
7422 inst.setConditionTaken(true);
7423
7424 /* Spread taint */
7425 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(pc, cf);
7426 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(pc, zf);
7427
7428 /* Create the path constraint */
7429 this->symbolicEngine->pushPathConstraint(inst, expr);
7430 }

7608 void x86Semantics::jg_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
7609 auto pc = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getProgramCounter());
7610 auto sf = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_SF));
7611 auto of = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_OF));
7612 auto zf = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ZF));
7613 auto srcImm1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(Immediate(inst.getNextAddress(), pc.getSize()));
7614 auto& srcImm2 = inst.operands[0];
7615
7616 /* Create symbolic operands */
7617 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, sf);
7618 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, of);
7619 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, zf);
7620 auto op4 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, srcImm1);
7621 auto op5 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, srcImm2);
7622
7623 /* Create the semantics */
7624 auto node = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->bvor(this->astCtxt->bvxor(op1, op2), op3), this->astCtxt->bvfalse()), op5, op4);
7625
7626 /* Create symbolic expression */
7627 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, pc, "Program Counter");
7628
7629 /* Set condition flag */
7630 if ((op1->evaluate().is_zero() == op2->evaluate().is_zero()) && op3->evaluate().is_zero())
7631 inst.setConditionTaken(true);
7632
7633 /* Spread taint */
7634 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(pc, sf);
7635 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(pc, of);
7636 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(pc, zf);
7637
7638 /* Create the path constraint */
7639 this->symbolicEngine->pushPathConstraint(inst, expr);
7640 }

7870 /* Set condition flag */
7871 if (op1->evaluate().is_zero())
7872 inst.setConditionTaken(true);
7873
7874 /* Spread taint */
7875 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(pc, sf);
7876
7877 /* Create the path constraint */
7878 this->symbolicEngine->pushPathConstraint(inst, expr);
7879 }

7882 void x86Semantics::jo_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
7883 auto pc = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getProgramCounter());
7884 auto of = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_OF));
7885 auto srcImm1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(Immediate(inst.getNextAddress(), pc.getSize()));
7886 auto& srcImm2 = inst.operands[0];
7887
7888 /* Create symbolic operands */
7889 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, of);
7890 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, srcImm1);
7891 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, srcImm2);
7892
7893 /* Create the semantics */
7894 auto node = this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(op1, this->astCtxt->bvtrue()), op3, op2);
7895
7896 /* Create symbolic expression */
7897 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, pc, "Program Counter");
7898
7899 /* Set condition flag */
7900 if (!op1->evaluate().is_zero())
7901 inst.setConditionTaken(true);
7902
7903 /* Spread taint */
7904 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(pc, of);
7905
7906 /* Create the path constraint */
7907 this->symbolicEngine->pushPathConstraint(inst, expr);
7908 }

7996
7997 void x86Semantics::lahf_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
7998 auto dst = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AH));
7999 auto src1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_SF));
8000 auto src2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ZF));
8001 auto src3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AF));
8002 auto src4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_PF));
8003 auto src5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_CF));
8004
8005 /* Create symbolic operands */
8006 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
8007 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
8008 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src3);
8009 auto op4 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src4);
8010 auto op5 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src5);
8011
8012 /* Create the semantics */
8013 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> flags;
8014 flags.reserve(8);
8015
8016 flags.push_back(op1);
8017 flags.push_back(op2);
8018 flags.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvfalse());
8019 flags.push_back(op3);
8020 flags.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvfalse());
8021 flags.push_back(op4);
8022 flags.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvtrue());
8023 flags.push_back(op5);
8024
8025 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(flags);
8026
8027 /* Create symbolic expression */
8028 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "LAHF operation");
8029
8030 /* Spread taint */
8031 this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src1);
8032 this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src2);
8033 this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src3);
8034 this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src4);
8035 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src5);
8036
8037 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
8038 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
8039 }

8077
8078 void x86Semantics::lea_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
8079 auto& dst = inst.operands[0].getRegister();
8080 auto& srcDisp = inst.operands[1].getMemory().getDisplacement();
8081 auto& srcBase = inst.operands[1].getMemory().getBaseRegister();
8082 auto& srcIndex = inst.operands[1].getMemory().getIndexRegister();
8083 auto& srcScale = inst.operands[1].getMemory().getScale();
8084 triton::uint32 leaSize = 0;
8085
8086 /* Setup LEA size */
8087 if (this->architecture->isRegisterValid(srcBase))
8088 leaSize = srcBase.getBitSize();
8089 else if (this->architecture->isRegisterValid(srcIndex))
8090 leaSize = srcIndex.getBitSize();
8091 else
8092 leaSize = srcDisp.getBitSize();
8093
8094 /* Create symbolic operands */
8095
8096 /* Displacement */
8097 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getImmediateAst(inst, srcDisp);
8098 if (leaSize > srcDisp.getBitSize())
8099 op2 = this->astCtxt->zx(leaSize - srcDisp.getBitSize(), op2);
8100
8101 /* Base */
8102 triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode op3 = nullptr;
8103 if (this->architecture->isRegisterValid(srcBase))
8104 op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getRegisterAst(inst, srcBase);
8105 else
8106 op3 = this->astCtxt->bv(0, leaSize);
8107
8108 /* Base with PC */
8109 if (this->architecture->isRegisterValid(srcBase) && (this->architecture->getParentRegister(srcBase) == this->architecture->getProgramCounter()))
8110 op3 = this->astCtxt->bvadd(op3, this->astCtxt->bv(inst.getSize(), leaSize));
8111
8112 /* Index */
8113 triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode op4 = nullptr;
8114 if (this->architecture->isRegisterValid(srcIndex))
8115 op4 = this->symbolicEngine->getRegisterAst(inst, srcIndex);
8116 else
8117 op4 = this->astCtxt->bv(0, leaSize);
8118
8119 /* Scale */
8120 auto op5 = this->symbolicEngine->getImmediateAst(inst, srcScale);
8121 if (leaSize > srcScale.getBitSize())
8122 op5 = this->astCtxt->zx(leaSize - srcScale.getBitSize(), op5);
8123
8124 /* Create the semantics */
8125 /* Effective address = Displacement + BaseReg + IndexReg * Scale */
8126 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvadd(op2, this->astCtxt->bvadd(op3, this->astCtxt->bvmul(op4, op5)));
8127
8128 if (dst.getBitSize() > leaSize)
8129 node = this->astCtxt->zx(dst.getBitSize() - leaSize, node);
8130
8131 if (dst.getBitSize() < leaSize)
8132 node = this->astCtxt->extract(dst.getHigh(), dst.getLow(), node);
8133
8134 /* Create symbolic expression */
8135 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicRegisterExpression(inst, node, dst, "LEA operation");
8136
8137 /* Spread taint */
8138 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->setTaint(dst, this->taintEngine->isTainted(srcBase) | this->taintEngine->isTainted(srcIndex));
8139
8140 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
8141 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
8142 }
8143
8144
8145 void x86Semantics::leave_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
8146 auto stack = this->architecture->getStackPointer();
8147 auto base = this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_BP);
8148 auto baseValue = static_cast<triton::uint64>(this->architecture->getConcreteRegisterValue(base));
8149 auto bp1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(baseValue, base.getSize()));
8150 auto bp2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_BP));
8151 auto sp = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(stack);
8152
8153 /* Create symbolic operands */
8154 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, bp2);
8155
8156 /* RSP = RBP */
8157 auto node1 = op1;
8158
8159 /* Create the symbolic expression */
8160 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, sp, "Stack Pointer");
8161
8162 /* Spread taint */
8163 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(sp, bp2);
8164
8165 /* Create symbolic operands */
8166 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, bp1);
8167
8168 /* RBP = pop() */
8169 auto node2 = op2;
8170
8171 /* Create the symbolic expression */
8172 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, bp2, "Stack Top Pointer");
8173
8174 /* Spread taint */
8175 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(bp2, bp1);
8176
8177 /* Create the semantics - side effect */
8178 alignAddStack_s(inst, bp1.getSize());
8179
8180 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
8181 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
8182 }

8185 void x86Semantics::lfence_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
8186 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
8187 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
8188 }

8190
8191 void x86Semantics::lodsb_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
8192 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
8193 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
8194 auto index = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_SI));
8195 auto cx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_CX));
8196 auto df = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_DF));
8197
8198 /* Check if there is a REP prefix and a counter to zero */
8199 if (inst.getPrefix() != triton::arch::x86::ID_PREFIX_INVALID && this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(cx)->evaluate().is_zero()) {
8200 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
8201 return;
8202 }
8203
8204 /* Create symbolic operands */
8205 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
8206 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, index);
8207 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, df);
8208
8209 /* Create the semantics */
8210 auto node1 = op1;
8211 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->ite(
8212 this->astCtxt->equal(op3, this->astCtxt->bvfalse()),
8213 this->astCtxt->bvadd(op2, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::byte, index.getBitSize())),
8214 this->astCtxt->bvsub(op2, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::byte, index.getBitSize()))
8215 );
8216
8217 /* Create symbolic expression */
8218 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, dst, "LODSB operation");
8219 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, index, "Index operation");
8220
8221 /* Spread taint */
8222 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
8223 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(index, index);
8224
8225 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
8226 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
8227 }

8346
8347 void x86Semantics::loop_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
8348 auto count = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_CX));
8349 auto pc = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getProgramCounter());
8350 auto& src = inst.operands[0];
8351
8352 /* Create symbolic operands */
8353 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
8354 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, count);
8355
8356 /* Create the semantics */
8357 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->ite(
8358 this->astCtxt->equal(op2, this->astCtxt->bv(0, op2->getBitvectorSize())),
8359 this->astCtxt->bv(inst.getNextAddress(), pc.getBitSize()),
8360 op1
8361 );
8362
8363 /* Create symbolic expression */
8364 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, pc, "Program Counter");
8365
8366 /* Set condition flag */
8367 if (op2->evaluate()) {
8368 inst.setConditionTaken(true);
8369 /* Spread taint */
8370 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(pc, count);
8371 }
8372 else {
8373 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(pc, src);
8374 }
8375
8376 /* Create the semantics */
8377 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->bvsub(op2, this->astCtxt->bv(1, op2->getBitvectorSize()));
8378
8379 /* Create symbolic expression */
8380 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, count, "LOOP counter operation");
8381
8382 /* Create the path constraint */
8383 this->symbolicEngine->pushPathConstraint(inst, expr1);
8384 }
8385
8386
8387 void x86Semantics::lzcnt_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
8388 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
8389 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
8390 auto bvSize1 = dst.getBitSize();
8391 auto bvSize2 = src.getBitSize();
8392
8393 /* Create symbolic operands */
8394 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
8395
8396 /* Create the semantics */
8397 triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode node = nullptr;
8398 switch (src.getSize()) {

8535 this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(bvSize2 - 59, bvSize2 - 59, op1), this->astCtxt->bvtrue()), this->astCtxt->bv(58, bvSize1),
8536 this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(bvSize2 - 60, bvSize2 - 60, op1), this->astCtxt->bvtrue()), this->astCtxt->bv(59, bvSize1),
8537 this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(bvSize2 - 61, bvSize2 - 61, op1), this->astCtxt->bvtrue()), this->astCtxt->bv(60, bvSize1),
8538 this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(bvSize2 - 62, bvSize2 - 62, op1), this->astCtxt->bvtrue()), this->astCtxt->bv(61, bvSize1),
8539 this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(bvSize2 - 63, bvSize2 - 63, op1), this->astCtxt->bvtrue()), this->astCtxt->bv(62, bvSize1),
8540 this->astCtxt->ite(this->astCtxt->equal(this->astCtxt->extract(bvSize2 - 64, bvSize2 - 64, op1), this->astCtxt->bvtrue()), this->astCtxt->bv(63, bvSize1),
8541 this->astCtxt->bv(64, bvSize1))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))))));
8542 break;
8543 default:
8544 throw triton::exceptions::Semantics("x86Semantics::lzcnt_s(): Invalid operand size.");
8545 }
8546
8547 /* Create symbolic expression */
8548 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "LZCNT operation");
8549
8550 /* Spread taint */
8551 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
8552
8553 /* Update symbolic flags */
8554 this->cfLzcnt_s(inst, expr, src, op1);
8555 this->zf_s(inst, expr, src);
8556
8557 /* Tag undefined flags */
8558 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_OF));
8559 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_SF));
8560 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_PF));
8561 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AF));
8562
8563 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
8564 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
8565 }
