8578
8579
8580 void x86Semantics::mov_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
8581 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
8582 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
8583 bool undef = false;
8584
8585 /* Create the semantics */
8586 auto node = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
8587
8588 /*
8589 * Special cases:
8590 *
8591 * Triton defines segment registers as 32 or 64 bits vector to
8592 * avoid to simulate the GDT which allows users to directly define
8593 * their segments offset.
8594 *
8595 * The code below, handles the case: MOV r/m{16/32/64}, Sreg
8596 */
8597 if (src.getType() == triton::arch::OP_REG) {
8598 uint32 id = src.getConstRegister().getId();
8599 if (id >= triton::arch::ID_REG_X86_CS && id <= triton::arch::ID_REG_X86_SS) {
8600 node = this->astCtxt->extract(dst.getBitSize()-1, 0, node);
8601 }
8602 if (id >= triton::arch::ID_REG_X86_CR0 && id <= triton::arch::ID_REG_X86_CR15) {
8603 undef = true;
8604 }
8605 }
8606
8607 /*
8608 * The code below, handles the case: MOV Sreg, r/m{16/32/64}
8609 */
8610 if (dst.getType() == triton::arch::OP_REG) {
8611 uint32 id = dst.getConstRegister().getId();
8612 if (id >= triton::arch::ID_REG_X86_CS && id <= triton::arch::ID_REG_X86_SS) {
8613 node = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::word-1, 0, node);
8614 }
8615 if (id >= triton::arch::ID_REG_X86_CR0 && id <= triton::arch::ID_REG_X86_CR15) {
8616 undef = true;
8617 }
8618 }
8619
8620 /* Create symbolic expression */
8621 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOV operation");
8622
8623 /* Spread taint */
8624 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
8625
8626 /* Tag undefined flags */
8627 if (undef) {
8628 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AF));
8629 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_CF));
8630 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_OF));
8631 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_PF));
8632 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_SF));
8633 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ZF));
8634 }
8635
8636 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
8637 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
8638 }
8639

8694
8695 void x86Semantics::movbe_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
8696 auto &dst = inst.operands[0];
8697 auto &src = inst.operands[1];
8698
8699 /* Create symbolic operands */
8700 auto op = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
8701
8702 /* Create the semantics */
8703 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> exprs;
8704 for (size_t i = 0; i < src.getSize(); ++i) {
8705 exprs.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::byte * i + (triton::bitsize::byte - 1),
8706 triton::bitsize::byte * i,
8707 op));
8708 }
8709 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(exprs);
8710
8711 /* Create symbolic expression */
8712 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVBE operation");
8713
8714 /* Spread taint */
8715 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
8716
8717 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
8718 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
8719 }
8720
8721
8722 void x86Semantics::movd_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
8723 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
8724 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
8725
8726 /* Create symbolic operands */
8727 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
8728
8729 /* Create the semantics */
8730 triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode node = nullptr;
8731
8732 switch (dst.getBitSize()) {
8733 /* GPR 32-bits */
8734 case triton::bitsize::dword:
8735 node = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dword-1, 0, op2);
8736 break;
8737
8738 /* MMX 64-bits */
8739 case triton::bitsize::qword:
8740 node = this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword, this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dword-1, 0, op2));
8741 break;
8742
8743 /* XMM 128-bits */
8744 case triton::bitsize::dqword:
8745 node = this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::qword + triton::bitsize::dword, this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dword-1, 0, op2));
8746 break;
8747 }
8748
8749 /* Create symbolic expression */
8750 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVD operation");
8751
8752 /* Update the x87 FPU Tag Word */
8753 if (dst.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::qword) {
8754 this->updateFTW(inst, expr);
8755 }
8756
8757 /* Spread taint */
8758 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
8759
8760 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
8761 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
8762 }
8763

8765 void x86Semantics::movddup_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {

8843 void x86Semantics::movhlps_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
8844 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
8845 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
8846
8847 /* Create symbolic operands */
8848 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
8849 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
8850
8851 /* Create the semantics */
8852 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(
8853 this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::dqword - 1), triton::bitsize::qword, op1), /* Destination[127..64] unchanged */
8854 this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::dqword - 1), triton::bitsize::qword, op2) /* Destination[63..0] = Source[127..64]; */
8855 );
8856
8857 /* Create symbolic expression */
8858 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVHLPS operation");
8859
8860 /* Spread taint */
8861 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
8862
8863 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
8864 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
8865 }

8868 void x86Semantics::movhpd_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
8869 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
8870 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
8871
8872 /* Create symbolic operands */
8873 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
8874 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
8875
8876 /* Create the semantics */
8877 triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode node = nullptr;
8878
8879 /* xmm, m64 */
8880 if (dst.getSize() == triton::size::dqword) {
8881 node = this->astCtxt->concat(
8882 this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::qword - 1), 0, op2), /* Destination[127..64] = Source */
8883 this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::qword - 1), 0, op1) /* Destination[63..0] unchanged */
8884 );
8885 }
8886
8887 /* m64, xmm */
8888 else {
8889 node = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::dqword - 1), triton::bitsize::qword, op2); /* Destination[63..00] = Source[127..64] */
8890 }
8891
8892 /* Create symbolic expression */
8893 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVHPD operation");
8894
8895 /* Spread taint */
8896 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
8897
8898 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
8899 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
8900 }

9065
9066 /* Create the semantics */
9067 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> signs;
9068 signs.reserve(4);
9069
9070 signs.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(127, 127, op2)); /* Destination[3] = Source[127]; */
9071 signs.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(95, 95, op2)); /* Destination[2] = Source[95]; */
9072 signs.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(63, 63, op2)); /* Destination[1] = Source[63]; */
9073 signs.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(31, 31, op2)); /* Destination[0] = Source[31]; */
9074
9075 auto node = this->astCtxt->zx(28, this->astCtxt->concat(signs));
9076
9077 /* Create symbolic expression */
9078 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVMSKPS operation");
9079
9080 /* Spread taint */
9081 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
9082
9083 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
9084 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
9085 }

9088 void x86Semantics::movntdq_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
9089 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
9090 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
9091

9180 auto& src = inst.operands[1];

9186 bytes.reserve(4);
9187
9188 bytes.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(127, 96, op2));
9189 bytes.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(127, 96, op2));
9190 bytes.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(63, 32, op2));
9191 bytes.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(63, 32, op2));
9192

9194
9195 /* Create symbolic expression */
9196 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVSHDUP operation");

9232
9233
9234 void x86Semantics::movq_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
9235 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
9236 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
9237
9238 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
9239 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
9240
9241 /* Create the semantics */
9242 triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode node = nullptr;
9243
9244 /* when operating on MMX technology registers and memory locations */
9245 if (dst.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::qword && src.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::qword)
9246 node = op2;
9247
9248 /* when source and destination operands are XMM registers */
9249 else if (dst.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::dqword && src.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::dqword)
9250 node = this->astCtxt->concat(
9251 this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dqword-1, triton::bitsize::qword, op1),
9252 this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::qword-1, 0, op2)
9253 );
9254
9255 /* when source operand is XMM register and destination operand is memory location */
9256 else if (dst.getBitSize() < src.getBitSize())
9257 node = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::qword-1, 0, op2);
9258
9259 /* when source operand is memory location and destination operand is XMM register */
9260 else if (dst.getBitSize() > src.getBitSize())
9261 node = this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::qword, op2);
9262
9263 /* Invalid operation */
9264 else
9265 throw triton::exceptions::Semantics("x86Semantics::movq_s(): Invalid operation.");
9266
9267 /* Create symbolic expression */
9268 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVQ operation");
9269
9270 /* Update the x87 FPU Tag Word */
9271 if (dst.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::qword && src.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::qword) {
9272 this->updateFTW(inst, expr);
9273 }
9274
9275 /* Spread taint */
9276 if (dst.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::dqword && src.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::dqword)
9277 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
9278 else
9279 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
9280
9281 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
9282 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
9283 }
9284
9285
9286 void x86Semantics::movq2dq_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
9287 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
9288 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
9289
9290 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
9291
9292 /* Create the semantics */
9293 auto node = this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::qword, op2);
9294
9295 /* Create symbolic expression */
9296 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVQ2DQ operation");
9297
9298 /* TODO @fvrmatteo: the x87 FPU top-of-stack pointer is set to 0 and the x87 FPU tag word is set to all 0s [valid] */
9299
9300 /* Spread taint */
9301 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
9302
9303 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
9304 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
9305 }

9307
9308 void x86Semantics::movsb_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
9309 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
9310 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
9311 auto index1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_DI));
9312 auto index2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_SI));
9313 auto cx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_CX));
9314 auto df = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_DF));
9315
9316 /* Check if there is a REP prefix and a counter to zero */
9317 if (inst.getPrefix() != triton::arch::x86::ID_PREFIX_INVALID && this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(cx)->evaluate().is_zero()) {
9318 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
9319 return;
9320 }
9321
9322 /* Create symbolic operands */
9323 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
9324 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, index1);
9325 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, index2);
9326 auto op4 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, df);
9327
9328 /* Create the semantics */
9329 auto node1 = op1;
9330 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->ite(
9331 this->astCtxt->equal(op4, this->astCtxt->bvfalse()),
9332 this->astCtxt->bvadd(op2, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::byte, index1.getBitSize())),
9333 this->astCtxt->bvsub(op2, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::byte, index1.getBitSize()))
9334 );
9335 auto node3 = this->astCtxt->ite(
9336 this->astCtxt->equal(op4, this->astCtxt->bvfalse()),
9337 this->astCtxt->bvadd(op3, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::byte, index2.getBitSize())),
9338 this->astCtxt->bvsub(op3, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::byte, index2.getBitSize()))
9339 );
9340
9341 /* Create symbolic expression */
9342 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, dst, "MOVSB operation");
9343 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, index1, "Index (DI) operation");
9344 auto expr3 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node3, index2, "Index (SI) operation");
9345
9346 /* Spread taint */
9347 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
9348 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(index1, index1);
9349 expr3->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(index2, index2);
9350
9351 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
9352 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
9353 }
9354
9355
9356 void x86Semantics::movsd_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
9357 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
9358 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
9359 auto index1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_DI));
9360 auto index2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_SI));
9361 auto cx = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getParentRegister(ID_REG_X86_CX));
9362 auto df = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_DF));
9363
9364 /* Check if there is a REP prefix and a counter to zero */
9365 if (inst.getPrefix() != triton::arch::x86::ID_PREFIX_INVALID && this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(cx)->evaluate().is_zero()) {
9366 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
9367 return;
9368 }
9369
9370 /*
9371 * F2 0F 10 /r MOVSD xmm1, xmm2
9372 * F2 0F 10 /r MOVSD xmm1, m64
9373 */
9374 if (dst.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::dqword) {
9375 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
9376 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(dst);
9377
9378 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(
9379 this->astCtxt->extract(127, 64, op2),
9380 this->astCtxt->extract(63, 0, op1)
9381 );
9382
9383 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVSD operation");
9384 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
9385 }
9386
9387 /*
9388 * F2 0F 11 /r MOVSD m64, xmm2
9389 */
9390 else if (dst.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::qword && src.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::dqword) {
9391 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
9392 auto node = this->astCtxt->extract(63, 0, op1);
9393 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVSD operation");
9394 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
9395 }
9396
9397 /* A5 MOVSD */
9398 else {
9399 /* Create symbolic operands */
9400 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
9401 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, index1);
9402 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, index2);
9403 auto op4 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, df);
9404
9405 /* Create the semantics */
9406 auto node1 = op1;
9407 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->ite(
9408 this->astCtxt->equal(op4, this->astCtxt->bvfalse()),
9409 this->astCtxt->bvadd(op2, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::dword, index1.getBitSize())),
9410 this->astCtxt->bvsub(op2, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::dword, index1.getBitSize()))
9411 );
9412 auto node3 = this->astCtxt->ite(
9413 this->astCtxt->equal(op4, this->astCtxt->bvfalse()),
9414 this->astCtxt->bvadd(op3, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::dword, index2.getBitSize())),
9415 this->astCtxt->bvsub(op3, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::dword, index2.getBitSize()))
9416 );
9417
9418 /* Create symbolic expression */
9419 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, dst, "MOVSD operation");
9420 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, index1, "Index (DI) operation");
9421 auto expr3 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node3, index2, "Index (SI) operation");
9422
9423 /* Spread taint */
9424 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
9425 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(index1, index1);
9426 expr3->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(index2, index2);
9427 }
9428
9429 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
9430 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
9431 }

9471 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
9472 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
9473

9475 auto op = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
9476
9477 /* Create the semantics */
9478 auto node = op;
9479 if (src.getType() == OP_REG) {
9480 node = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dword - 1, 0, node);
9481 if (dst.getType() == OP_REG) {
9482 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
9483 auto upper = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dqword - 1, triton::bitsize::dword, op1);
9484 node = this->astCtxt->concat(upper, node);
9485 }
9486 }
9487
9488 /* Create symbolic expression */
9489 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVSS operation");
9490
9491 /* Spread taint */
9492 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
9493
9494 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
9495 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
9496 }

9616 void x86Semantics::movsxd_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
9617 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
9618 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
9619
9620 /* Create symbolic operands */
9621 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
9622
9623 /* Create the semantics */
9624 auto node = this->astCtxt->sx(dst.getBitSize() - src.getBitSize(), op1);
9625
9626 /* Create symbolic expression */
9627 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVSXD operation");
9628
9629 /* Spread taint */
9630 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
9631
9632 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
9633 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
9634 }
9635
9636
9637 void x86Semantics::movzx_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
9638 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
9639 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
9640
9641 /* Create symbolic operands */
9642 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
9643
9644 /* Create the semantics */
9645 auto node = this->astCtxt->zx(dst.getBitSize() - src.getBitSize(), op1);
9646
9647 /* Create symbolic expression */
9648 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MOVZX operation");
9649
9650 /* Spread taint */
9651 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
9652
9653 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
9654 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
9655 }
9656
9657
9658 void x86Semantics::mul_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
9659 auto& src2 = inst.operands[0];
9660
9661 switch (src2.getSize()) {
9662
9663 /* AX = AL * r/m8 */
9664 case triton::size::byte: {
9665 auto dst = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
9666 auto src1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AL));
9667 /* Create symbolic operands */
9668 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
9669 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
9670 /* Create the semantics */
9671 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvmul(this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::byte, op1), this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::byte, op2));
9672 /* Create symbolic expression */
9673 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "MUL operation");
9674 /* Apply the taint */
9675 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src2);
9676 /* Update symbolic flags */
9677 auto ah = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::word - 1), triton::bitsize::byte, node);
9678 this->cfMul_s(inst, expr, src2, ah);
9679 this->ofMul_s(inst, expr, src2, ah);
9680 break;
9681 }
9682
9683 /* DX:AX = AX * r/m16 */
9684 case triton::size::word: {
9685 auto dst1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
9686 auto dst2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_DX));
9687 auto src1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AX));
9688 /* Create symbolic operands */
9689 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
9690 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
9691 /* Create symbolic expression for ax */
9692 auto ax = this->astCtxt->bvmul(op1, op2);
9693 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, ax, dst1, "MUL operation");
9694 /* Apply the taint */
9695 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst1, src2);
9696 /* Create symbolic expression for dx */
9697 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvmul(this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::word, op1), this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::word, op2));
9698 auto dx = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::dword - 1), triton::bitsize::word, node);
9699 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, dx, dst2, "MUL operation");
9700 /* Apply the taint */
9701 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst2, src2);
9702 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst2, src1);
9703 /* Update symbolic flags */
9704 this->cfMul_s(inst, expr2, src2, dx);
9705 this->ofMul_s(inst, expr2, src2, dx);
9706 break;
9707 }
9708
9709 /* EDX:EAX = EAX * r/m32 */
9710 case triton::size::dword: {
9711 auto dst1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EAX));
9712 auto dst2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EDX));
9713 auto src1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EAX));
9714 /* Create symbolic operands */
9715 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
9716 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
9717 /* Create symbolic expression for eax */
9718 auto eax = this->astCtxt->bvmul(op1, op2);
9719 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, eax, dst1, "MUL operation");
9720 /* Apply the taint */
9721 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst1, src2);
9722 /* Create symbolic expression for edx */
9723 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvmul(this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword, op1), this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword, op2));
9724 auto edx = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::qword - 1), triton::bitsize::dword, node);
9725 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, edx, dst2, "MUL operation");
9726 /* Apply the taint */
9727 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst2, src2);
9728 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst2, src1);
9729 /* Update symbolic flags */
9730 this->cfMul_s(inst, expr2, src2, edx);
9731 this->ofMul_s(inst, expr2, src2, edx);
9732 break;
9733 }
9734
9735 /* RDX:RAX = RAX * r/m64 */
9736 case triton::size::qword: {
9737 auto dst1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RAX));
9738 auto dst2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RDX));
9739 auto src1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RAX));
9740 /* Create symbolic operands */
9741 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
9742 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
9743 /* Create the semantics */
9744 /* Create symbolic expression for eax */
9745 auto rax = this->astCtxt->bvmul(op1, op2);
9746 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, rax, dst1, "MUL operation");
9747 /* Apply the taint */
9748 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst1, src2);
9749 /* Create symbolic expression for rdx */
9750 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvmul(this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::qword, op1), this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::qword, op2));
9751 auto rdx = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::dqword - 1), triton::bitsize::qword, node);
9752 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, rdx, dst2, "MUL operation");
9753 /* Apply the taint */
9754 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst2, src2);
9755 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst2, src1);
9756 /* Update symbolic flags */
9757 this->cfMul_s(inst, expr2, src2, rdx);
9758 this->ofMul_s(inst, expr2, src2, rdx);
9759 break;
9760 }
9761
9762 }
9763
9764 /* Tag undefined flags */
9765 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AF));
9766 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_PF));
9767 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_SF));
9768 this->undefined_s(inst, this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ZF));
9769
9770 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
9771 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
9772 }
9773
9774
9775 void x86Semantics::mulx_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
9776 switch (inst.operands[0].getSize()) {
9777
9778 /* r32a, r32b, r/m32 */
9779 case triton::size::dword: {
9780 auto& dst1 = inst.operands[0];
9781 auto& dst2 = inst.operands[1];
9782 auto src1 = inst.operands[2];
9783 auto src2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EDX));
9784
9785 /* Create symbolic operands */
9786 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
9787 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
9788
9789 /* Create the semantics */
9790 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvmul(this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword, op1), this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword, op2));
9791 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(op1, op2);
9792 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::qword - 1), triton::bitsize::dword, node);
9793
9794 /* Create symbolic expression */
9795 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, dst2, "MULX operation");
9796 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, dst1, "MULX operation");
9797
9798 /* Apply the taint */
9799 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst2, src1);
9800 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst2, src2);
9801
9802 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst1, src1);
9803 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst1, src2);
9804 break;
9805 }
9806
9807 /* r64a, r64b, r/m64 */
9808 case triton::size::qword: {
9809 auto& dst1 = inst.operands[0];
9810 auto& dst2 = inst.operands[1];
9811 auto src1 = inst.operands[2];
9812 auto src2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RDX));
9813
9814 /* Create symbolic operands */
9815 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
9816 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
9817
9818 /* Create the semantics */
9819 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvmul(this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::qword, op1), this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::qword, op2));
9820 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(op1, op2);
9821 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->extract((triton::bitsize::dqword - 1), triton::bitsize::qword, node);
9822
9823 /* Create symbolic expression for eax */
9824 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, dst2, "MULX operation");
9825 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, dst1, "MULX operation");
9826
9827 /* Apply the taint */
9828 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst2, src1);
9829 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst2, src2);
9830
9831 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst1, src1);
9832 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst1, src2);
9833 break;
9834 }
9835
9836 }
9837
9838 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
9839 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
9840 }

9924 /* Update the symbolic control flow */

9972
9973 void x86Semantics::packuswb_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
9974 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
9975 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
9976
9977 /* Create symbolic operands */
9978 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
9979 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
9980
9981 /* Create the semantics */
9982 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> pck;
9983 pck.reserve(dst.getSize());
9984
9985 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> ops{op2, op1};
9986 for (triton::uint32 i = 0; i < ops.size(); i++) {
9987 for (triton::uint32 index = 0; index < dst.getSize() / triton::size::word; index++) {
9988 uint32 high = (dst.getBitSize() - 1) - (index * triton::bitsize::word);
9989 uint32 low = (dst.getBitSize() - triton::bitsize::word) - (index * triton::bitsize::word);
9990 auto signed_word = this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, ops[i]);
9991 pck.push_back(this->astCtxt->ite(
9992 this->astCtxt->bvsge(signed_word, this->astCtxt->bv(0xff, triton::bitsize::word)),
9993 this->astCtxt->bv(0xff, triton::bitsize::byte),
9994 this->astCtxt->ite(
9995 this->astCtxt->bvsle(signed_word, this->astCtxt->bv(0x00, triton::bitsize::word)),
9996 this->astCtxt->bv(0x00, triton::bitsize::byte),
9997 this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::byte - 1, 0, signed_word)))
9998 );
9999 }
10000 }
10001
10002 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(pck);
10003
10004 /* Create symbolic expression */
10005 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PACKUSWB operation");
10006
10007 /* Apply the taint */
10008 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
10009
10010 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
10011 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
10012 }

10014
10015 void x86Semantics::packssdw_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
10016 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
10017 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
10018
10019 /* Create symbolic operands */
10020 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
10021 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
10022
10023 /* Create the semantics */
10024 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> pck;
10025 pck.reserve(dst.getSize() / triton::size::word);
10026
10027 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> ops{op2, op1};
10028
10029 for (triton::uint32 idx = 0; idx < ops.size(); ++idx) {
10030 for (triton::uint32 i = 0; i < dst.getSize() / triton::size::dword; ++i) {
10031 uint32 high = (dst.getBitSize() - 1) - (i * triton::bitsize::dword);
10032 uint32 low = (dst.getBitSize() - triton::bitsize::dword) - (i * triton::bitsize::dword);
10033 auto signed_dword = this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, ops[idx]);
10034 pck.push_back(this->astCtxt->ite(
10035 this->astCtxt->bvsge(signed_dword, this->astCtxt->bv(0x7fff, triton::bitsize::dword)),
10036 this->astCtxt->bv(0x7fff, triton::bitsize::word),
10037 this->astCtxt->ite(
10038 this->astCtxt->bvsle(signed_dword, this->astCtxt->bv(0xffff8000, triton::bitsize::dword)),
10039 this->astCtxt->bv(0x8000, triton::bitsize::word),
10040 this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::word - 1, 0, signed_dword)))
10041 );
10042 }
10043 }
10044
10045 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(pck);
10046
10047 /* Create symbolic expression */
10048 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PACKSSDW operation");
10049
10050 /* Apply the taint */
10051 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
10052
10053 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
10054 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
10055 }

10098
10099
10100 void x86Semantics::paddb_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
10101 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
10102 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
10103
10104 /* Create symbolic operands */
10105 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
10106 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
10107
10108 /* Create the semantics */
10109 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> packed;
10110 packed.reserve(16);
10111
10112 switch (dst.getBitSize()) {
10113
10114 /* XMM */
10115 case triton::bitsize::dqword:
10116 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(127, 120, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(127, 120, op2)));
10117 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(119, 112, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(119, 112, op2)));
10118 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(111, 104, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(111, 104, op2)));
10119 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(103, 96, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(103, 96, op2)));
10120 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(95, 88, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(95, 88, op2)));
10121 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(87, 80, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(87, 80, op2)));
10122 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(79, 72, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(79, 72, op2)));
10123 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(71, 64, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(71, 64, op2)));
10124
10125 /* MMX */
10126 case triton::bitsize::qword:
10127 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(63, 56, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(63, 56, op2)));
10128 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(55, 48, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(55, 48, op2)));
10129 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(47, 40, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(47, 40, op2)));
10130 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(39, 32, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(39, 32, op2)));
10131 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(31, 24, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(31, 24, op2)));
10132 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(23, 16, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(23, 16, op2)));
10133 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(15, 8, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(15, 8, op2)));
10134 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(this->astCtxt->extract(7, 0, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(7, 0, op2)));
10135 break;
10136
10137 default:
10138 throw triton::exceptions::Semantics("x86Semantics::paddb_s(): Invalid operand size.");
10139
10140 }
10141
10142 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(packed);
10143
10144 /* Create symbolic expression */
10145 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PADDB operation");
10146
10147 /* Update the x87 FPU Tag Word */
10148 if (dst.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::qword) {
10149 this->updateFTW(inst, expr);
10150 }
10151
10152 /* Spread taint */
10153 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
10154
10155 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
10156 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
10157 }

10305
10306 void x86Semantics::palignr_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
10307 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
10308 auto& src1 = inst.operands[1];
10309 auto& src2 = inst.operands[2];
10310
10311 /* Create symbolic operands */
10312 auto size = 2 * dst.getBitSize();
10313 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
10314 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
10315 auto op3 = this->astCtxt->zx(size - src2.getBitSize(), this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2));
10316
10317 /* Create the semantics */
10318 auto node = this->astCtxt->extract(
10319 dst.getBitSize() - 1, 0,
10320 this->astCtxt->bvlshr(
10321 this->astCtxt->concat(op1, op2),
10322 this->astCtxt->bvmul(
10323 this->astCtxt->ite(
10324 this->astCtxt->bvuge(op3, this->astCtxt->bv(2 * dst.getSize(), size)),
10325 this->astCtxt->bv(2 * dst.getSize(), size),
10326 op3),
10327 this->astCtxt->bv(triton::bitsize::byte, size)
10328 )));
10329
10330 /* Create symbolic expression */
10331 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PALIGNR operation");
10332
10333 /* Spread taint */
10334 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src1);
10335
10336 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
10337 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
10338 }

10397 void x86Semantics::pavgb_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
10398 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
10399 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
10400
10401 /* Create symbolic operands */
10402 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
10403 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
10404
10405 /* Create the semantics */
10406 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> pck;
10407 pck.reserve(dst.getSize());
10408
10409 for (triton::uint32 index = 0; index < dst.getSize(); index++) {
10410 uint32 high = (dst.getBitSize() - 1) - (index * triton::bitsize::byte);
10411 uint32 low = (dst.getBitSize() - triton::bitsize::byte) - (index * triton::bitsize::byte);
10412 pck.push_back(
10413 this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::byte-1, 0,
10414 this->astCtxt->bvlshr(
10415 this->astCtxt->bvadd(
10416 this->astCtxt->bvadd(
10417 this->astCtxt->zx(1, this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op1)),
10418 this->astCtxt->zx(1, this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op2))
10419 ),
10420 this->astCtxt->bv(1, triton::bitsize::byte+1)
10421 ),
10422 this->astCtxt->bv(1, triton::bitsize::byte+1)
10423 )
10424 )
10425 );
10426 }
10427
10428 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(pck);
10429
10430 /* Create symbolic expression */
10431 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PAVGB operation");
10432
10433 /* Spread taint */
10434 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
10435
10436 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
10437 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
10438 }

10667 }

10670 void x86Semantics::pcmpgtw_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
10671 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
10672 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
10673
10674 /* Create symbolic operands */
10675 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
10676 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
10677
10678 /* Create the semantics */
10679 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> pck;
10680 pck.reserve(dst.getSize());
10681
10682 for (triton::uint32 index = 0; index < dst.getSize() / triton::size::word; index++) {
10683 uint32 high = (dst.getBitSize() - 1) - (index * triton::bitsize::word);
10684 uint32 low = (dst.getBitSize() - triton::bitsize::word) - (index * triton::bitsize::word);
10685 pck.push_back(this->astCtxt->ite(
10686 this->astCtxt->bvsgt(
10687 this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op1),
10688 this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op2)),
10689 this->astCtxt->bv(0xffff, triton::bitsize::word),
10690 this->astCtxt->bv(0x0000, triton::bitsize::word))
10691 );
10692 }
10693
10694 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(pck);
10695
10696 /* Create symbolic expression */
10697 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PCMPGTW operation");
10698
10699 /* Apply the taint */
10700 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
10701
10702 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
10703 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
10704 }

10827
10828 void x86Semantics::pextrw_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
10829 triton::uint32 count = 0;
10830 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
10831 auto& src1 = inst.operands[1];
10832 auto& src2 = inst.operands[2];
10833
10834 /*
10835 * When specifying a word location in an MMX technology register, the
10836 * 2 least-significant bits of the count operand specify the location;
10837 * for an XMM register, the 3 least-significant bits specify the
10838 * location.
10839 */
10840 if (src1.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::qword) {
10841 count = 0x03;
10842 }
10843 else {
10844 count = 0x07;
10845 }
10846
10847 /* Create symbolic operands */
10848 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
10849 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
10850 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
10851
10852 auto node = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::word - 1, 0,
10853 this->astCtxt->bvlshr(
10854 op2,
10855 this->astCtxt->bv(((op3->evaluate() & count) * triton::bitsize::word), op2->getBitvectorSize())
10856 )
10857 );
10858
10859 /* Create symbolic expression */
10860 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PEXTRW operation");
10861
10862 /* Apply the taint */
10863 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src1);
10864
10865 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
10866 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
10867 }
10868
10869
10870 void x86Semantics::pinsrb_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
10871 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
10872 auto& src1 = inst.operands[1];
10873 auto& src2 = inst.operands[2];
10874
10875 /* Create symbolic operands */
10876 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
10877 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
10878 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
10879
10880 // SEL = COUNT[3:0];
10881 // MASK = (0FFH << (SEL * 8));
10882 triton::uint64 sel = static_cast<triton::uint64>(op3->evaluate()) & 0x0f;
10883 triton::uint128 mask = 0xff;
10884 mask = mask << (sel * 8);
10885
10886 // TEMP = ((SRC[7:0] << (SEL * 8)) AND MASK);
10887 auto temp = this->astCtxt->bvand(
10888 this->astCtxt->bvshl(
10889 this->astCtxt->zx(120, this->astCtxt->extract(7, 0, op2)),
10890 this->astCtxt->bv(sel * 8, 128)
10891 ),
10892 this->astCtxt->bv(mask, 128)
10893 );
10894
10895 // DEST = ((DEST AND NOT MASK) OR TEMP);
10896 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvor(
10897 this->astCtxt->bvand(
10898 op1,
10899 this->astCtxt->bvnot(this->astCtxt->bv(mask, 128))
10900 ),
10901 temp
10902 );
10903
10904 /* Create symbolic expression */
10905 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PINSRB operation");
10906
10907 /* Apply the taint */
10908 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src1);
10909
10910 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
10911 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
10912 }

10960 void x86Semantics::pinsrq_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
10961 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
10962 auto& src1 = inst.operands[1];

10969
10970 // SEL = COUNT[0:0];
10971 // MASK = (0FFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFH << (SEL * 64));
10972 triton::uint64 sel = static_cast<triton::uint64>(op3->evaluate()) & 0x1;
10973 triton::uint128 mask = 0xffffffffffffffff;
10974 mask = mask << (sel * 64);
10975

10977 auto temp = this->astCtxt->bvand(
10978 this->astCtxt->bvshl(
10979 this->astCtxt->zx(64, this->astCtxt->extract(63, 0, op2)),
10980 this->astCtxt->bv(sel * 64, 128)
10981 ),
10982 this->astCtxt->bv(mask, 128)
10983 );
10984
10985 // DEST = ((DEST AND NOT MASK) OR TEMP);
10986 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvor(
10987 this->astCtxt->bvand(
10988 op1,
10989 this->astCtxt->bvnot(this->astCtxt->bv(mask, 128))
10990 ),
10991 temp
10992 );
10993
10994 /* Create symbolic expression */
10995 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PINSRQ operation");
10996
10997 /* Apply the taint */
10998 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src1);
10999
11000 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
11001 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
11002 }
11003
11004
11005 void x86Semantics::pinsrw_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
11006 triton::uint128 mask = 0xffff;
11007 triton::uint64 sel = 0;
11008 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
11009 auto& src1 = inst.operands[1];
11010 auto& src2 = inst.operands[2];
11011
11012 /* Create symbolic operands */
11013 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
11014 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
11015 auto op3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
11016
11017 /*
11018 * PINSRW (with 64-bit source operand)
11019 *
11020 * SEL = COUNT AND 3H;
11021 * CASE (Determine word position) {
11022 * if SEL == 0: MASK = 000000000000FFFFH;
11023 * if SEL == 1: MASK = 00000000FFFF0000H;
11024 * if SEL == 2: MASK = 0000FFFF00000000H;
11025 * if SEL == 3: MASK = FFFF000000000000H;
11026 * }
11027 */
11028 if (dst.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::qword) {
11029 sel = static_cast<triton::uint64>(op3->evaluate()) & 0x3;
11030 switch (sel) {
11031 case 1: mask = mask << 16; break;
11032 case 2: mask = mask << 32; break;
11033 case 3: mask = mask << 48; break;
11034 }
11035 }
11036
11037 /*
11038 * PINSRW (with 128-bit source operand)
11039 *
11040 * SEL ← COUNT AND 7H;
11041 * CASE (Determine word position) {
11042 * SEL == 0: MASK = 0000000000000000000000000000FFFFH;
11043 * SEL == 1: MASK = 000000000000000000000000FFFF0000H;
11044 * SEL == 2: MASK = 00000000000000000000FFFF00000000H;
11045 * SEL == 3: MASK = 0000000000000000FFFF000000000000H;
11046 * SEL == 4: MASK = 000000000000FFFF0000000000000000H;
11047 * SEL == 5: MASK = 00000000FFFF00000000000000000000H;
11048 * SEL == 6: MASK = 0000FFFF000000000000000000000000H;
11049 * SEL == 7: MASK = FFFF0000000000000000000000000000H;
11050 * }
11051 */
11052 else {
11053 sel = static_cast<triton::uint64>(op3->evaluate()) & 0x7;
11054 switch (sel) {
11055 case 1: mask = mask << 16; break;
11056 case 2: mask = mask << 32; break;
11057 case 3: mask = mask << 48; break;
11058 case 4: mask = mask << 64; break;
11059 case 5: mask = mask << 80; break;
11060 case 6: mask = mask << 96; break;
11061 case 7: mask = mask << 112; break;
11062 }
11063 }
11064
11065 // TEMP = ((SRC << (SEL ∗ 16)) AND MASK);
11066 auto temp = this->astCtxt->bvand(
11067 this->astCtxt->bvshl(
11068 this->astCtxt->zx(112, this->astCtxt->extract(15, 0, op2)),
11069 this->astCtxt->bv(sel * 16, 128)
11070 ),
11071 this->astCtxt->bv(mask, 128)
11072 );
11073
11074 // DEST = ((DEST AND NOT MASK) OR TEMP);
11075 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvor(
11076 this->astCtxt->bvand(
11077 op1,
11078 this->astCtxt->bvnot(this->astCtxt->bv(mask, 128))
11079 ),
11080 temp
11081 );
11082
11083 /* Create symbolic expression */
11084 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PINSRW operation");
11085
11086 /* Apply the taint */
11087 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src1);
11088
11089 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
11090 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
11091 }
11092
11093
11094 void x86Semantics::pmaddwd_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
11095 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
11096 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
11097
11098 /* Create symbolic operands */
11099 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
11100 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
11101
11102 /* Create the semantics */
11103 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> pck;
11104 pck.reserve(dst.getSize() / triton::size::dword);
11105
11106 for (triton::uint32 i = 0; i < dst.getSize() / triton::size::word; i += 2) {
11107 uint32 high = (dst.getBitSize() - 1) - (i * triton::bitsize::word);
11108 uint32 low = (dst.getBitSize() - triton::bitsize::word) - (i * triton::bitsize::word);
11109 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(
11110 this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::word, this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op1)),
11111 this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::word, this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op2))
11112 );
11113 high -= triton::bitsize::word;
11114 low -= triton::bitsize::word;
11115 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->bvmul(
11116 this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::word, this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op1)),
11117 this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::word, this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op2))
11118 );
11119 pck.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvadd(node1, node2));
11120 }
11121
11122 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(pck);
11123
11124 /* Create symbolic expression */
11125 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PMADDWD operation");
11126
11127 /* Apply the taint */
11128 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
11129
11130 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
11131 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
11132 }

11248 auto& src = inst.operands[1];

11250 /* Create symbolic operands */
11251 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
11252 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
11253
11254 /* Create the semantics */
11255 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> pck;
11256 pck.reserve(dst.getSize());
11257
11258 for (triton::uint32 index = 0; index < dst.getSize() / triton::size::dword; index++) {
11259 uint32 high = (dst.getBitSize() - 1) - (index * triton::bitsize::dword);
11260 uint32 low = (dst.getBitSize() - triton::bitsize::dword) - (index * triton::bitsize::dword);
11261 pck.push_back(this->astCtxt->ite(
11262 this->astCtxt->bvule(
11263 this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op1),
11264 this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op2)),
11265 this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op2),
11266 this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op1))
11267 );
11268 }
11269
11270 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(pck);
11271
11272 /* Create symbolic expression */
11273 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PMAXUD operation");
11274
11275 /* Apply the taint */
11276 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
11277
11278 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
11279 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
11280 }

11541
11542 void x86Semantics::pmovmskb_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
11543 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
11544 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
11545
11546 /* Create symbolic operands */
11547 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
11548
11549 /* Create the semantics */
11550 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> mskb;
11551 mskb.reserve(16);
11552
11553 switch (src.getSize()) {
11554 case triton::size::dqword:
11555 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(127, 127, op2));
11556 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(119, 119, op2));
11557 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(111, 111, op2));
11558 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(103, 103, op2));
11559 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(95, 95, op2));
11560 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(87, 87, op2));
11561 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(79, 79, op2));
11562 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(71, 71, op2));
11563
11564 case triton::size::qword:
11565 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(63, 63, op2));
11566 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(55, 55, op2));
11567 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(47, 47, op2));
11568 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(39, 39, op2));
11569 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(31, 31, op2));
11570 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(23, 23, op2));
11571 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(15, 15, op2));
11572 mskb.push_back(this->astCtxt->extract(7, 7, op2));
11573 }
11574
11575 auto node = this->astCtxt->zx(
11576 dst.getBitSize() - static_cast<triton::uint32>(mskb.size()),
11577 this->astCtxt->concat(mskb)
11578 );
11579
11580 /* Create symbolic expression */
11581 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PMOVMSKB operation");
11582
11583 /* Apply the taint */
11584 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
11585
11586 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
11587 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
11588 }

11776 pck.push_back(this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword - triton::bitsize::byte, this->astCtxt->extract(15, 8, op2)));
11777 pck.push_back(this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword - triton::bitsize::byte, this->astCtxt->extract(7, 0, op2)));
11778
11779 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(pck);
11780
11781 /* Create symbolic expression */
11782 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PMOVZXBD operation");
11783
11784 /* Apply the taint */
11785 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
11786
11787 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
11788 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
11789 }

11934
11935 void x86Semantics::pmulhw_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
11936 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
11937 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
11938
11939 /* Create symbolic operands */
11940 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
11941 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
11942
11943 /* Create the semantics */
11944 if ((!op1->isSymbolized() && op1->evaluate() == 0) ||
11945 (!op2->isSymbolized() && op2->evaluate() == 0)) {
11946 auto node = this->astCtxt->bv(0, dst.getBitSize());
11947 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PMULHW operation");
11948 this->taintEngine->setTaint(dst, false);
11949 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
11950 return;
11951 }
11952
11953 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> pck;
11954 pck.reserve(dst.getSize() / triton::size::word);
11955
11956 for (triton::uint32 i = 0; i < dst.getSize() / triton::size::word; ++i) {
11957 uint32 high = (dst.getBitSize() - 1) - (i * triton::bitsize::word);
11958 uint32 low = (dst.getBitSize() - triton::bitsize::word) - (i * triton::bitsize::word);
11959 auto n1 = this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::word, this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op1));
11960 auto n2 = this->astCtxt->sx(triton::bitsize::word, this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op2));
11961 auto node = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dword - 1, triton::bitsize::word, this->astCtxt->bvmul(n1, n2));
11962 pck.push_back(node);
11963 }
11964 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(pck);
11965
11966 /* Create symbolic expression */
11967 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PMULHW operation");
11968
11969 /* Apply the taint */
11970 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
11971
11972 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
11973 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
11974 }

12061 void x86Semantics::popcnt_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
12062 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
12063 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
12064
12065 /* Create symbolic operands */
12066 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
12067 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
12068
12069 /* Create the semantics */
12070 auto node = this->astCtxt->bv(0, dst.getBitSize());
12071 for (triton::uint32 i = 0; i < src.getBitSize(); ++i) {
12072 node = this->astCtxt->bvadd(
12073 node,
12074 this->astCtxt->zx(dst.getBitSize() - 1, this->astCtxt->extract(i, i, op2))
12075 );
12076 }
12077
12078 /* Create symbolic expression */
12079 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "POPCNT operation");
12080
12081 /* Spread taint */
12082 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
12083
12084 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
12085 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
12086 }
12087
12088
12089 void x86Semantics::pop_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
12090 bool stackRelative = false;
12091 auto stack = this->architecture->getStackPointer();
12092 auto stackValue = static_cast<triton::uint64>(this->architecture->getConcreteRegisterValue(stack));
12093 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
12094 auto src = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(stackValue, dst.getSize()));
12095
12096 /* Create symbolic operands */
12097 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
12098
12099 /* Create the semantics */
12100 auto node = op1;
12101
12102 /*
12103 * Create the semantics - side effect
12104 *
12105 * Intel: If the ESP register is used as a base register for addressing a destination operand in
12106 * memory, the POP instruction computes the effective address of the operand after it increments
12107 * the ESP register.
12108 */
12109 if (dst.getType() == triton::arch::OP_MEM) {
12110 const triton::arch::Register& base = dst.getMemory().getConstBaseRegister();
12111 /* Check if the base register is the stack pointer */
12112 if (this->architecture->isRegisterValid(base) && this->architecture->getParentRegister(base) == stack) {
12113 /* Align the stack */
12114 alignAddStack_s(inst, src.getSize());
12115 /* Re-initialize the memory access */
12116 this->symbolicEngine->initLeaAst(dst.getMemory());
12117 stackRelative = true;
12118 }
12119 }
12120
12121 /*
12122 * Create the semantics - side effect
12123 *
12124 * Don't increment SP if the destination register is SP.
12125 */
12126 else if (dst.getType() == triton::arch::OP_REG) {
12127 if (this->architecture->getParentRegister(dst.getRegister()) == stack) {
12128 stackRelative = true;
12129 }
12130 }
12131
12132 /* Create symbolic expression */
12133 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "POP operation");
12134
12135 /* Spread taint */
12136 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
12137
12138 /* Create the semantics - side effect */
12139 if (!stackRelative)
12140 alignAddStack_s(inst, src.getSize());
12141
12142 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
12143 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
12144 }
12145
12146
12147 void x86Semantics::popal_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
12148 auto stack = this->architecture->getStackPointer();
12149 auto stackValue = static_cast<triton::uint64>(this->architecture->getConcreteRegisterValue(stack));
12150 auto dst1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EDI));
12151 auto dst2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ESI));
12152 auto dst3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EBP));
12153 auto dst4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EBX));
12154 auto dst5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EDX));
12155 auto dst6 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ECX));
12156 auto dst7 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_EAX));
12157 auto src1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(stackValue+(stack.getSize() * 0), stack.getSize()));
12158 auto src2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(stackValue+(stack.getSize() * 1), stack.getSize()));
12159 auto src3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(stackValue+(stack.getSize() * 2), stack.getSize()));
12160 /* stack.getSize() * 3 (ESP) is voluntarily omitted */
12161 auto src4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(stackValue+(stack.getSize() * 4), stack.getSize()));
12162 auto src5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(stackValue+(stack.getSize() * 5), stack.getSize()));
12163 auto src6 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(stackValue+(stack.getSize() * 6), stack.getSize()));
12164 auto src7 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(stackValue+(stack.getSize() * 7), stack.getSize()));
12165
12166 /* Create symbolic operands and semantics */
12167 auto node1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src1);
12168 auto node2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src2);
12169 auto node3 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src3);
12170 auto node4 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src4);
12171 auto node5 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src5);
12172 auto node6 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src6);
12173 auto node7 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src7);
12174
12175 /* Create symbolic expression */
12176 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, dst1, "POPAL EDI operation");
12177 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, dst2, "POPAL ESI operation");
12178 auto expr3 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node3, dst3, "POPAL EBP operation");
12179 auto expr4 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node4, dst4, "POPAL EBX operation");
12180 auto expr5 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node5, dst5, "POPAL EDX operation");
12181 auto expr6 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node6, dst6, "POPAL ECX operation");
12182 auto expr7 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node7, dst7, "POPAL EAX operation");
12183
12184 /* Spread taint */
12185 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst1, src1);
12186 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst2, src2);
12187 expr3->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst3, src3);
12188 expr4->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst4, src4);
12189 expr5->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst5, src5);
12190 expr6->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst6, src6);
12191 expr7->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst7, src7);
12192
12193 /* Create the semantics - side effect */
12194 alignAddStack_s(inst, stack.getSize() * 8);
12195
12196 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
12197 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
12198 }
12199
12200
12201 void x86Semantics::popf_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
12202 auto stack = this->architecture->getStackPointer();
12203 auto stackValue = static_cast<triton::uint64>(this->architecture->getConcreteRegisterValue(stack));
12204 auto dst1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_CF));
12205 auto dst2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_PF));
12206 auto dst3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AF));
12207 auto dst4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ZF));
12208 auto dst5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_SF));
12209 auto dst6 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_TF));
12210 auto dst7 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_IF));
12211 auto dst8 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_DF));
12212 auto dst9 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_OF));
12213 auto dst10 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_NT));
12214 auto src = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(stackValue, stack.getSize()));
12215
12216 /* Create symbolic operands */
12217 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
12218
12219 /* Create the semantics */
12220 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->extract(0, 0, op1);
12221 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->extract(2, 2, op1);
12222 auto node3 = this->astCtxt->extract(4, 4, op1);
12223 auto node4 = this->astCtxt->extract(6, 6, op1);
12224 auto node5 = this->astCtxt->extract(7, 7, op1);
12225 auto node6 = this->astCtxt->extract(8, 8, op1);
12226 auto node7 = this->astCtxt->bvtrue(); /* IF true? */
12227 auto node8 = this->astCtxt->extract(10, 10, op1);
12228 auto node9 = this->astCtxt->extract(11, 11, op1);
12229 /* IOPL don't support */
12230 auto node10 = this->astCtxt->extract(14, 14, op1);
12231
12232 /* Create symbolic expression */
12233 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, dst1.getRegister(), "POPF CF operation");
12234 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, dst2.getRegister(), "POPF PF operation");

12238 auto expr6 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node6, dst6.getRegister(), "POPF TF operation");
12239 auto expr7 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node7, dst7.getRegister(), "POPF IF operation");
12240 auto expr8 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node8, dst8.getRegister(), "POPF DF operation");
12241 auto expr9 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node9, dst9.getRegister(), "POPF OF operation");
12242 auto expr10 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node10, dst10.getRegister(), "POPF NT operation");
12243
12244 /* Spread taint */
12245 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst1, src);
12246 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst2, src);
12247 expr3->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst3, src);

12253 expr9->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst9, src);
12254 expr10->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst10, src);
12255
12256 /* Create the semantics - side effect */

12258
12259 /* Update the symbolic control flow */

12264 void x86Semantics::popfd_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
12265 auto stack = this->architecture->getStackPointer();
12266 auto stackValue = static_cast<triton::uint64>(this->architecture->getConcreteRegisterValue(stack));
12267 auto dst1 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_CF));
12268 auto dst2 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_PF));
12269 auto dst3 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AF));
12270 auto dst4 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ZF));
12271 auto dst5 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_SF));
12272 auto dst6 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_TF));
12273 auto dst7 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_IF));
12274 auto dst8 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_DF));
12275 auto dst9 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_OF));
12276 auto dst10 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_NT));
12277 auto dst11 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_RF));
12278 auto dst12 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_AC));
12279 auto dst13 = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(this->architecture->getRegister(ID_REG_X86_ID));
12280 auto src = triton::arch::OperandWrapper(triton::arch::MemoryAccess(stackValue, stack.getSize()));
12281
12282 /* Create symbolic operands */
12283 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
12284
12285 /* Create the semantics */
12286 auto node1 = this->astCtxt->extract(0, 0, op1);
12287 auto node2 = this->astCtxt->extract(2, 2, op1);
12288 auto node3 = this->astCtxt->extract(4, 4, op1);
12289 auto node4 = this->astCtxt->extract(6, 6, op1);
12290 auto node5 = this->astCtxt->extract(7, 7, op1);
12291 auto node6 = this->astCtxt->extract(8, 8, op1);
12292 auto node7 = this->astCtxt->bvtrue(); /* IF true? */
12293 auto node8 = this->astCtxt->extract(10, 10, op1);
12294 auto node9 = this->astCtxt->extract(11, 11, op1);
12295 /* IOPL don't support */
12296 auto node10 = this->astCtxt->extract(14, 14, op1);
12297 auto node11 = this->astCtxt->bvfalse(); /* RF clear */
12298 /* VM not changed */
12299 auto node12 = this->astCtxt->extract(18, 18, op1);
12300 /* VIP not changed */
12301 /* VIF not changed */
12302 auto node13 = this->astCtxt->extract(21, 21, op1);
12303
12304 /* Create symbolic expression */
12305 auto expr1 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node1, dst1.getRegister(), "POPFD CF operation");
12306 auto expr2 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node2, dst2.getRegister(), "POPFD PF operation");
12307 auto expr3 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node3, dst3.getRegister(), "POPFD AF operation");
12308 auto expr4 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node4, dst4.getRegister(), "POPFD ZF operation");
12309 auto expr5 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node5, dst5.getRegister(), "POPFD SF operation");
12310 auto expr6 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node6, dst6.getRegister(), "POPFD TF operation");
12311 auto expr7 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node7, dst7.getRegister(), "POPFD IF operation");
12312 auto expr8 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node8, dst8.getRegister(), "POPFD DF operation");
12313 auto expr9 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node9, dst9.getRegister(), "POPFD OF operation");
12314 auto expr10 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node10, dst10.getRegister(), "POPFD NT operation");
12315 auto expr11 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node11, dst11.getRegister(), "POPFD RF operation");
12316 auto expr12 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node12, dst12.getRegister(), "POPFD AC operation");
12317 auto expr13 = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node13, dst13.getRegister(), "POPFD ID operation");
12318
12319 /* Spread taint */
12320 expr1->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst1, src);
12321 expr2->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst2, src);
12322 expr3->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst3, src);
12323 expr4->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst4, src);
12324 expr5->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst5, src);
12325 expr6->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst6, src);
12326 expr7->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst7, src);
12327 expr8->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst8, src);
12328 expr9->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst9, src);
12329 expr10->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst10, src);
12330 expr11->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst11, src);
12331 expr12->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst12, src);
12332 expr13->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst13, src);
12333
12334 /* Create the semantics - side effect */

12337 /* Update the symbolic control flow */

12420 void x86Semantics::por_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
12421 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
12422 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
12423
12424 /* Create symbolic operands */
12425 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
12426 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
12427
12428 /* Create the semantics */
12429 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvor(op1, op2);
12430
12431 /* Create symbolic expression */
12432 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "POR operation");
12433
12434 /* Update the x87 FPU Tag Word */
12435 this->updateFTW(inst, expr);
12436
12437 /* Spread taint */
12438 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
12439
12440 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
12441 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
12442 }

12486 this->astCtxt->bv(32, triton::bitsize::dqword)
12487 )
12488 )
12489 )

12497 this->astCtxt->bv(32, triton::bitsize::dqword)
12498 )
12499 )
12500 )
12501 );

12504 this->astCtxt->bvlshr(
12505 op2,
12506 this->astCtxt->bvmul(

12703 this->astCtxt->bvmul(
12704 this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::qword-2, this->astCtxt->extract(5, 4, op3)),
12705 this->astCtxt->bv(16, triton::bitsize::qword)
12706 )
12707 )
12708 )
12709 );
12710 pack.push_back(
12711 this->astCtxt->extract(15, 0,
12712 this->astCtxt->bvlshr(
12713 op2,
12714 this->astCtxt->bvmul(
12715 this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::qword-2, this->astCtxt->extract(3, 2, op3)),
12716 this->astCtxt->bv(16, triton::bitsize::qword)
12717 )
12718 )
12719 )
12720 );
12721 pack.push_back(
12722 this->astCtxt->extract(15, 0,
12723 this->astCtxt->bvlshr(
12724 op2,
12725 this->astCtxt->bvmul(
12726 this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::qword-2, this->astCtxt->extract(1, 0, op3)),
12727 this->astCtxt->bv(16, triton::bitsize::qword)
12728 )
12729 )
12730 )
12731 );
12732
12733 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(pack);
12734
12735 /* Create symbolic expression */
12736 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PSHUFW operation");
12737
12738 /* Spread taint */
12739 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintAssignment(dst, src);
12740
12741 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
12742 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
12743 }

12745
12746 void x86Semantics::pslld_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
12747 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
12748 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
12749
12750 /* Create symbolic operands */
12751 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
12752 auto op2 = this->astCtxt->zx(dst.getBitSize() - src.getBitSize(), this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src));
12753
12754 /* Create the semantics */
12755 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> packed;
12756 packed.reserve(4);
12757
12758 switch (dst.getBitSize()) {
12759 /* XMM */
12760 case triton::bitsize::dqword:
12761 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvshl(this->astCtxt->extract(127, 96, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(31, 0, op2)));
12762 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvshl(this->astCtxt->extract( 95, 64, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(31, 0, op2)));
12763
12764 /* MMX */
12765 case triton::bitsize::qword:
12766 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvshl(this->astCtxt->extract(63, 32, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(31, 0, op2)));
12767 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvshl(this->astCtxt->extract(31, 0, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(31, 0, op2)));
12768 break;
12769
12770 default:
12771 throw triton::exceptions::Semantics("x86Semantics::pslld_s(): Invalid operand size.");
12772 }
12773
12774 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(packed);
12775
12776 /* Create symbolic expression */
12777 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PSLLD operation");
12778
12779 /* Update the x87 FPU Tag Word */
12780 if (dst.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::qword) {
12781 this->updateFTW(inst, expr);
12782 }
12783
12784 /* Spread taint */
12785 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
12786
12787 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
12788 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
12789 }

12792 void x86Semantics::pslldq_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
12793 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
12794 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
12795
12796 /* Create symbolic operands */
12797 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
12798 auto op2 = this->astCtxt->zx(dst.getBitSize() - src.getBitSize(), this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src));
12799
12800 /* Create the semantics */
12801 auto node = this->astCtxt->bvshl(
12802 op1,
12803 this->astCtxt->bvmul(
12804 this->astCtxt->ite(
12805 this->astCtxt->bvuge(op2, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::bitsize::word, dst.getBitSize())),
12806 this->astCtxt->bv(triton::bitsize::word, dst.getBitSize()),
12807 op2
12808 ),
12809 this->astCtxt->bv(triton::size::qword, dst.getBitSize())
12810 )
12811 );
12812
12813 /* Create symbolic expression */
12814 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PSLLDQ operation");
12815
12816 /* Spread taint */
12817 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
12818
12819 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
12820 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
12821 }

12824 void x86Semantics::psllq_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
12825 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
12826 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
12827
12828 /* Create symbolic operands */
12829 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
12830 auto op2 = this->astCtxt->zx(dst.getBitSize() - src.getBitSize(), this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src));
12831
12832 /* Create the semantics */
12833 triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode node;
12834
12835 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> packed;
12836 packed.reserve(2);
12837
12838 switch (dst.getBitSize()) {
12839 /* XMM */
12840 case triton::bitsize::dqword:
12841 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvshl(this->astCtxt->extract(127, 64, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(63, 0, op2)));
12842 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvshl(this->astCtxt->extract( 63, 0, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(63, 0, op2)));
12843 node = this->astCtxt->concat(packed);
12844 break;
12845
12846 /* MMX */
12847 case triton::bitsize::qword:
12848 /* MMX register is only one QWORD so it's a simple shl */
12849 node = this->astCtxt->bvshl(op1, op2);
12850 break;
12851
12852 default:
12853 throw triton::exceptions::Semantics("x86Semantics::psllq_s(): Invalid operand size.");
12854 }
12855
12856 /* Create symbolic expression */
12857 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PSLLQ operation");
12858
12859 /* Update the x87 FPU Tag Word */
12860 if (dst.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::qword) {
12861 this->updateFTW(inst, expr);
12862 }
12863
12864 /* Spread taint */
12865 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
12866
12867 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
12868 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
12869 }

12872 void x86Semantics::psllw_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {

12874 auto& src = inst.operands[1];

12888 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvshl(this->astCtxt->extract(111, 96, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(15, 0, op2)));

12891

12895 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvshl(this->astCtxt->extract(47, 32, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(15, 0, op2)));
12896 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvshl(this->astCtxt->extract(31, 16, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(15, 0, op2)));
12897 packed.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvshl(this->astCtxt->extract(15, 0, op1), this->astCtxt->extract(15, 0, op2)));

12906 /* Create symbolic expression */

12908
12909 /* Update the x87 FPU Tag Word */
12910 if (dst.getBitSize() == triton::bitsize::qword) {
12911 this->updateFTW(inst, expr);
12912 }
12913
12914 /* Spread taint */
12915 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);

12921
12922 void x86Semantics::psrad_s(triton::arch::Instruction& inst) {
12923 auto& dst = inst.operands[0];
12924 auto& src = inst.operands[1];
12925
12926 /* Create symbolic operands */
12927 auto op1 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, dst);
12928 auto op2 = this->symbolicEngine->getOperandAst(inst, src);
12929
12930 /* Create the semantics */
12931 std::vector<triton::ast::SharedAbstractNode> pck;
12932 pck.reserve(dst.getSize() / triton::size::dword);
12933
12934 auto shift = this->astCtxt->ite(
12935 this->astCtxt->bvuge(op2, this->astCtxt->bv(triton::bitsize::dword, src.getBitSize())),
12936 this->astCtxt->bv(triton::bitsize::dword, src.getBitSize()),
12937 op2
12938 );
12939
12940 if (shift->getBitvectorSize() < triton::bitsize::dword) {
12941 shift = this->astCtxt->zx(triton::bitsize::dword - shift->getBitvectorSize(), shift);
12942 }
12943 else {
12944 shift = this->astCtxt->extract(triton::bitsize::dword - 1, 0, shift);
12945 }
12946
12947 for (triton::uint32 i = 0; i < dst.getSize() / triton::size::dword; ++i) {
12948 uint32 high = (dst.getBitSize() - 1) - (i * triton::bitsize::dword);
12949 uint32 low = (dst.getBitSize() - triton::bitsize::dword) - (i * triton::bitsize::dword);
12950 pck.push_back(this->astCtxt->bvashr(this->astCtxt->extract(high, low, op1), shift));
12951 }
12952 auto node = this->astCtxt->concat(pck);
12953
12954 /* Create symbolic expression */
12955 auto expr = this->symbolicEngine->createSymbolicExpression(inst, node, dst, "PSRAD operation");
12956
12957 /* Spread taint */
12958 expr->isTainted = this->taintEngine->taintUnion(dst, src);
12959
12960 /* Update the symbolic control flow */
12961 this->controlFlow_s(inst);
12962 }
